uds with Vistara</h2>\r\n<h3>Do you have control across your dynamic resources?</h3>\r\n<p>Enterprise services today depend on resources that reside in the cloud and on-premise. You are responsible for the service no matter what goes down and you need a single place that provides complete visibility and control of that Hybrid IT environment. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vistara lets you connect your public and private cloud resources to construct a complete picture of your critical applications, whether they are built entirely with dynamic cloud resources or in a hybrid environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"inside-boxs\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-123\" alt=\"Amazon Web Services\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/amazon.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\" /><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/gcplogo.png\" alt=\"Google Cloud Platform\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3810\" /><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/windows-azure1.png\" alt=\"windows-azure\" width=\"160\" height=\"53\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3809\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-124\" alt=\"Rackspace\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/rockspace.png\" width=\"140\" height=\"50\" />\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-124\" alt=\"OpenStack\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/OpenStackc.png\" width=\"140\" height=\"50\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n<h3>Manage Any Cloud Resource</h3>\r\n<p>Whether it’s public or private cloud, compute or any other resource, Vistara allows you to manage any cloud element in a unified platform</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Manage AWS, Google Cloud, Microsoft Azure and other cloud assets</li>\r\n<li>Manage across AWS resources such as ELB, Auto Scaling Groups, Route 53, DynamoDB, RDS, SNS, SQS and EBS\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\