starait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Automation-Policies-Giff.gif\" alt=\"Controlled Change Management\"/>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n<h4>Automate Ops with Policies</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Define automation policies for self remediation of common issues before escalating as an incident</li>\r\n<li>Define scheduled and event-driven runbook automation scripts and policies and schedules to execute</li>\r\n<li>Leverage built-in library of commonly used RBA scripts</li>\r\n<li>Use scripting language of choice including Shell, PowerShell, Python, Perl, Windows Command Scripts, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n<h4>Control Access by Role</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Restrict the operations that a user can perform at the user and user group, devices and device group, credentials, permissions and permission sets, or role level</li>\r\n<li>Credentials can be managed and assigned to devices with policies</li> \r\n<li>Define fine-grained escalation policies based on schedule or notification types to route incoming alerts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Role-Based-Access-Controls.gif\" alt=\"Controlled Change Management\"/>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n<img style=\"padding:35px 0 0 0;\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/manage-patch.gif\" alt=\"Patch Management and Network Configuration Policy\"/>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n<h4>Manage Patching and Network Configuration Policy</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Automatically scan servers and clients at discovery to determine patch level compliance with enterprise policies</li>\r\n<li>Patch Windows and Linux servers, desktops and laptops throughout distributed sites</li>\r\n<li>Define sophisticated patch policies and apply multiple policies to a single element</li>\r\n<li>Deploy and update any application, antivirus agents and its signatures</li>\r\n<li>Automatically backup network device configurations</li>\r\n<li>Compare configurations to identify changes and restore to previous configurations when needed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n<h4>Manage Holistic Services from Top to Bottom</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Service maps created using flexible rule based policies</li>\r\n<li>Expands and shrinks dynamically with new elements or instances or decommissioned elements</li>\r\n<li>Define services based on the availability or set of metrics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Servic-Maps.gif\" alt=\"Policy Based Service Maps\"/>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Dashboard.gif\" alt=\"Customizable Dashboards and Reporting\"/>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n<h4>See the Metrics That Matter To You</h4>\r\n<ul><li>Customizable dashboards with widgets defined by complete service or single entity</li>\r\n<li>Define your own widgets (value, list, time series) or use predefined widgets</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"section-colored\">\r\n			<div class=\"container ds-devopsbx\">\r\n<h2>Browse Our DevOps Resources</h2>\r\n				<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05