r\n<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\r\n<li class=\"active\" data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"0\"></li>\r\n<li data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\r\n<li data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\r\n<li data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"3\"></li>\r\n<li data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"4\"></li>\r\n<li data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"5\"></li>\r\n<li data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"6\"></li>\r\n<li data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"7\"></li>\r\n<li data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"8\"></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<div class=\"carousel-inner\">\r\n<div class=\"item active\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-965\" alt=\"Public Cloud Management\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Public-Cloud-Management1.jpg\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Public Cloud Management</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p><span>Automatically discover all virtual machine instances in the public cloud and monitor and manage them.</span></p>\r\n<p>Manage multiple instances of public clouds from various cloud service providers in a single view.</p>\r\n<p>Categorize instances based on criteria such as provider and location to ease navigation.</p>\r\n<p>Create deployment profiles based on <span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"d2e9bcae-762c-4378-9fa5-119ba8142ad7\">deployed</span> instances, then easily create new instances.</p>\r\n<p>Sessions between Vistara and public clouds are 256 <span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"755b9f7b-5358-418a-b742-2b887fba3b54\">bit SSL encrypted to</span> ensure security.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-972\" alt=\"OpenStack Support Gives Customers Freedom of-Choice in Public Cloud Services\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/OpenStack-Support-Gives-Customers-Freedom-of-Choice-in-Public-Cloud-Services.jpg\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"9f66d3cf-a923-4f81-8f49-1c5fecccdaca\">OpenStack</span> Support Gives Customers Freedom of Choice in Public Cloud Services</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"92bdaffc-c2a5-4b2a-a75c-87480c2895c0\">Vistara</span> supports OpenStack to enable cloud management and application portability without vendor lock-in. </p>\r\n<p>Vistara’s implementation of OpenStack enables a self-service portal and removes the manual work involved in deploying servers.</p>\r\n<p>Manage your distributed resources as one computing pool where applications and workloads can be provisioned and decommissioned on demand.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-975\" alt=\"Supported Public Clouds\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Supported-Public-Clouds.jpg\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Supported Public Clouds</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p>Vistara supports the following public clouds for delivering unified IT operations management:</p>\r\n<p>Amazon EC2</p>\r\n<p>Rackspace Open Cloud</p>\r\n<p>Microsoft Azure</p>\r\n<p>OpenStack-based clouds</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-971\" alt=\"Private Cloud Management\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Private-Cloud-Management1.jpg\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Private Cloud Management</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p>Vistara offers everything you need to quickly and easily monitor, manage, grow, and optimize your private cloud in a single, integrated, software-as-a-service solution.</p>\r\n<p>Quickly discover, monitor and manage storage, virtual machines, and servers as they are dynamically provisioned on demand and bring them under control. Vistara gives you a faster path to delivering a private cloud solution.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-970\" alt=\"Converged Infrastructure Management\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Converged-Infrastructure-Management.jpg\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Converged Infrastructure Management</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p>Vistara manages your private cloud whether you use converged infrastructure solutions, your own choice of hardware, or a mixture.</p>\r\n<p>Monitor, and manage leading converged infrastructure solutions such as EMC® VSPEX® or NetApp® FlexPod®.</p>\r\n<p>Visualize the complete solution and easily browse to inspect and manage any element.</p>\r\n<p>Easily add, monitor, manage, and remove any element from the solution including storage, servers and switches.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-969\" alt=\"Storage Management\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Storage-Management.jpg\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Storage Management</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p>Monitor and manage leading storage solutions such as EMC VNX®/VNXe®, NetApp FAS®, and more.</p>\r\n<p>Monitor storage pools, volumes, and total storage capacity through the dashboard.</p>\r\n<p>Automatically detect when storage utilization thresholds are being exceeded in time to provision additional storage.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-968\" alt=\"Virtualization Management\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Virtualization-Management.jpg\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Virtualization Management</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p>Start, suspend, and stop virtual machines.</p>\r\n<p>Automatically discover the topology of the virtualized environments; use visual maps to show relationships between virtual machines, hypervisors, SAN fabrics, storage arrays, and virtual and physical networks.</p>\r\n<p>Monitor virtual machines, hypervisors, storage elements, and networks.</p>\r\n<p>Monitor key performance indicators including I/O latencies, storage space usage, CPU usage, memory usage, and most active virtual machines (by CPU, memory, or storage usage) through the dashboard.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-967\" alt=\"Hybrid Cloud Management\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Hybrid-Cloud-Management.jpg\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Hybrid Cloud Management</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p>Monitor and manage multiple private clouds and public clouds and federate them together into a hybrid cloud through a single solution.</p>\r\n<p>Use a single solution to provide visibility, manage IT processes, and measure service levels across both private and public cloud resources.</p>\r\n<p> Vistara provides the same monitoring and management capabilities for instances deployed on the private cloud and on public clouds.</p>\r\n<p>Vendor-neutral solution provisions, monitors and manages hardware, software, virtual machines, and cloud services from multiple providers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-966\" alt=\"Easy Management Through Software as a Service\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Easy-Management-Through-Software-as-a-Service.jpg\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Easy Management Through Software as a Service</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p>Agentless management of your private cloud, storage solution, compute layer, switches, and virtual machines.</p>\r\n<p>Solution automatically upgrades itself.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Cloud Management','','publish','open','open','','cloud-management','','','2014-07-14 13:16:24','2014-07-14 13:16:24','',93,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=750',0,'page','',0),(756,1,'2014-03-18 11:17:39','2014-03-18 11:17:39','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\" class=\"leafnode-nav\"><div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"what-we-do-menu\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div></section><section id=\"discovery-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"page-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h1>Asset Management</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"section\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n       <div class=\"heading