lass=\"leafnode-nav\"><div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"what-we-do-menu\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div></section>\r\n<section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"heading-box\">\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214\" alt=\"Application Management\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/application.png\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" /></p>\r\n<h1>Application Management</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"big-font\">One of the key challenges in a large IT environment is managing the diverse set of applications in the enterprise. IT users require a wide range of applications supported at the highest level of availability. Because different teams in an enterprise have different application version requirements, the application landscape gets crowded and difficult to manage. Vistara addresses these challenges by providing robust application support capabilities.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"custom-post-slider\">\r\n<div class=\"carousel slide carousel-fade\" id=\"carousel-example-generic\" data-interval=\"true\" data-ride=\"carousel\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"carousel-outer\">\r\n<ol class=\"carousel-indicators\">\r\n<li class=\"active\" data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"0\"></li>\r\n<li data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"1\"></li>\r\n<li data-target=\"#carousel-example-generic\" data-slide-to=\"2\"></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<div class=\"carousel-inner\">\r\n<div class=\"item active\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Application-Monitoring-and-Management.jpg\" alt=\"Application Monitoring and Management\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-979\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Application Monitoring and Management</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p>Rich set of monitoring templates for a wide range of IT applications which satisfy key requirements such as application health status monitoring, process monitoring, file monitoring, and log monitoring.</p>\r\n<p>Configure monitoring to do simple data collection for trend analysis or to generate alerts to enable higher order correlation of the application’s status.</p>\r\n<p>Combine the rich set of templates with Vistara’s runbook automation capability for a single point of control for application management needs in an enterprise.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Versioned-Monitoring-Templates.jpg\" alt=\"Versioned Monitoring Templates\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-980\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Versioned Monitoring Templates</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p>Majority of IT environments have multiple versions of the same application serving IT users simultaneously. This is necessary due to application feature needs, IT budget constraints, user training needs, and external commitments.</p>\r\n<p>Vistara’s monitoring templates are customized for specific versions of the major applications. This helps IT teams support multiple versions of the IT applications for distinct internal teams.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-7 carousel-img\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Synthetic-Transactions-for-Applications-and-Components.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Synthetic-Transactions-for-Applications-and-Components.jpg\" alt=\"Synthetic Transactions for Applications and Components\" width=\"402\" height=\"304\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-981\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-md-5 carousel-text\">\r\n<h2>Synthetic Transactions for Applications and Components</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<p>Vistara employs synthetic transactions to determine the availability of an application. However, the most critical element of application management is to determine the health of the individual components of the application. Each component should evaluate the health of all components that it depends on.</p>\r\n<p>Vistara employs a rich set of synthetic transactions to measure the health of these components. This gives a higher level visibility to IT teams enabling them to predict and diagnose any issues easily.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Application Management','','publish','open','open','','application-management','','','2014-04-16 13:32:14','2014-04-16 13:32:14','',93,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=766',0,'page','',0),(796,1,'2014-03-18 12:31:41','2014-03-18 12:31:41','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\" class=\"leafnode-nav\"><div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"what-we-do-menu\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div></section><section id=\"discovery-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"page-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h1>Discovery</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"section\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n       <div class=\"heading-box\" id=\"product-box\">\r\n          <h4 class=\"alignleft col-sm-10\">Vistara allows you to automatically discover devices, applications and the relationships between them using standard protocols and APIs.</h4><div class=\"alignright col-sm-1\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/product/vistara-lifecycle-management/\"><img class=\"rotate\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/wheel.png\" alt=\"Back to Overview\" title=\"Back to Overview\"></a></div>\r\n       </div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div