a: A Self-Guided Tour</a> (Interactive Flash Demo)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-9\">\r\n\r\nVistara 3.0 features new support for hybrid service definition, monitoring, and management to support today’s hybrid IT operations model and the ability to customize its administrator dashboard so your team can focus on what matters most. It also supports custom escalation matrixes and the ability to manage assets over their lifecycle.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n<p class=\"right-img\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2866\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IT-Operations-Management-with-Vistara.png\" alt=\"IT-Operations-Management-with-Vistara\" width=\"193\" height=\"117\" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/it-operations-management-with-vistara-an-overview\" target=\"_blank\">IT Operations Management with Vistara: An Overview </a>(Video Demo)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-9\">\r\n\r\nVistara’s support for role-based access controls gives IT administrators and line of business users different views of its management capabilities.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n<p class=\"right-img\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2866\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Unified-IT-Operations-Management.png\" alt=\"Unified IT Operations Management\" width=\"193\" height=\"117\" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/managing-microsoft-applications-with-vistara\" target=\"_blank\">Managing Microsoft Applications with Vistara</a> (Video Demo)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-9\">\r\n\r\nVistara can do patch and configuration management and realtime status monitoring and management for Microsoft® applications such as Microsoft Exchange®, Microsoft Active Directory®, and more.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n<p class=\"right-img\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2866\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Microsoft-Application-Management.png\" alt=\"IT-Operations-Management-with-Vistara\" width=\"193\" height=\"117\" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/managing-emc-vspex-converged-infrastructure-solution-and-brocade-vdx-and-icx-with-vistara\" target=\"_blank\">Managing EMC VSPEX Converged Infrastructure Solution and Brocade VDX and ICX® with Vistara</a> (Flash Demo)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-9\">\r\n\r\nSee Vistara manage the EMC® VSPEX® converged infrastructure solution and a Brocade® VDX® switch.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n<p class=\"right-img\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2866\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/EMC-VSPEX-Management.png\" alt=\"EMC VSPEX Management\" width=\"193\" height=\"117\" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/managing-netapp-flexpod-converged-infrastructure-solutions-and-fas-storage-solutions-with-vistara\" target=\"_blank\">Managing NetApp® FlexPod® Converged Infrastructure Solutions and FAS® Storage Solutions with Vistara</a> (Video Demo)</p>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-2866 alignright\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica neue\', Arial, sans-serif; text-align: right;\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/NetApp-Flexpod-Management.png\" alt=\"NetApp Flexpod Management\" width=\"193\" height=\"117\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">Vistara enables you to easily manage NetApp® FAS® storage solutions and to easily manage private clouds based on NetApp FlexPod converged infrastructure solutions. Manage all elements of the FlexPod-based stack inc