s collect anonymous information from visits to our sites to help us provide better customer service. For example, we keep track of the domains from which people visit and we also measure visitor activity on VistaraIT, Inc. web sites, but we do so in ways that keep the information anonymous. VistaraIT, Inc. or its affiliates or vendors may use this data to analyze trends and statistics and to help us provide better customer service. We maintain the highest levels of confidentiality for this information, our affiliates and vendors follow the same high levels of confidentiality. This anonymous information is used and analyzed only at an aggregate level to help us understand trends and patterns. None of this information is reviewed at an individual level. If you do not want your transaction details used in this manner, you can either disable your cookies or opt-out at the download or request page.</p>\r\n<p class=\"big-font\">Mailers</p>\r\n<p>VistaraIT, Inc. may, if you so choose, send direct mailers to you at the address given by you. You have the option to ‘opt-out’ of this direct mailer by way of links provided at the bottom of each mailer. We respect your privacy and in the event that you choose to not receive such mailers, we will take all steps to remove you from the list.</p>\r\n<p class=\"big-font\">AntiSpam policy</p>\r\n<p>VistaraIT, Inc. recognizes the receipt, transmission or distribution of spam emails (unsolicited bulk emails) as a major concern and has taken reasonable measures, to minimize the transmission and effect of spam emails in its computing environment. All emails received by VistaraIT, Inc., are subject to spam check, in coordination with “SPAMHAUS” subscription service. Any email identified as spam will be rejected with sufficient information to the Sender for taking necessary action. With this measure, along with other technical spam reduction measures, VistaraIT, Inc. hopes to minimize the effect of spam emails. VistaraIT, Inc. reserves the right to reject and/or report any suspicious spam emails, to the authorities concerned, for necessary action, from time to time.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Privacy Policy','','publish','open','open','','privacy','','','2014-07-15 10:37:26','2014-07-15 10:37:26','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=1360',0,'page','',0),(1363,1,'2014-03-22 11:47:16','2014-03-22 11:47:16','','Blog','','publish','open','open','','blog','','','2014-04-04 14:26:19','2014-04-04 14:26:19','',670,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=1363',0,'page','',0),(1368,42,'2014-03-20 00:00:31','2014-03-20 00:00:31','<p><a href=\"http://www.data-corporation.com\"><img class=\" wp-image-2965 alignright\" alt=\"DATACORP-Logo\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/DATACORP-Logo.png\" width=\"298\" height=\"149\" /></a>When Data Corporation, a South Florida technology company, saw the potential opportunities and challenges that cloud computing would bring to enterprise IT, they shifted their focus from IT projects to managing IT for clients who struggled to resource their IT the way their business demanded. But it wasn’t easy to build a managed services practice that anticipated the customer needs of tomorrow with the existing tool sets that were limited in their scope, difficult to use, and just too many.</p>\r\n<p>Then they tried Vistara.</p>\r\n<p>DATACORP engineers can now identify potential customer issues and proactively act to resolve problems before they impact the customer’s business. Robust alerting and dashboards in Vistara empower DATACORP to capture incidents across a customer’s IT infrastructure, assess business impact through service mapping, and act. They can also do it in one single pane of glass, rather than the multiple tools that they used before.</p>\r\n<p>Terrisa McMillan, Director of Consulting for DATACORP says, “Vistara provides greater visibility into our clients’ environment, letting us manage our clients more effectively and efficiently. With Vistara, not only has our customer satisfaction gone up, but also we are able to manage more customers and companies with the engineers that we have. Vistara has increased profitability, consistency and insight. The solution pays for itself in preventing downtime for our customers. It allows me to be a better managed service provider.”</p>\r\n<p>Vistara is the ideal solution to build a managed service practice - that’s what it was made for. The technology was conceived to support multiple enterprise IT customer environments. After a decade of refining its functionality to best serve the enterprise as a service provider, the robust multi tenant SaaS software with end-to-end IT lifecycle management capabilities was born as Vistara.</p>\r\n<p>Terrisa and DATACORP have been fantastic partners to prove how Vistara can help a managed service provider raise the bar for proactive service, engineering productivity, and customer satisfaction. Many thanks to the great team at DATACORP! Read more about their story <a title=\"DATACORP Case Study\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/resources/casestudies/datacorp/\">here</a>.</p>','DATACORP Transforms Their Managed Service Business with Vistara','','publish','open','open','','managed-service-providers-business-transformation','','','2014-09-19 04:42:38','2014-09-19 04:42:38','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=1368',0,'post','',0),(1371,42,'2014-03-06 01:55:03','2014-03-06 01:55:03','<p>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Blog-Post-Service-Monitoring-for-Modern-IT-Operations2.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2968 alignright\" alt=\"Service Monitoring for Modern IT Operations\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Blog-Post-Service-Monitoring-for-Modern-IT-Operations2.jpg\" width=\"345\" height=\"230\" /></a>As IT organizations transform from technology <span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"9ffd5e31-46ec-47b3-843d-0ce97263d521\">integrators</span> into service providers, they must be able to be able to accurately monitor the state of a service so it can be managed proactively rather than reactively. Services are becoming ever more complex because they are constructed from a combination of elements that are on-premise, on private clouds, <span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"0f669ed0-d44d-4db8-bdf7-456ecae49dd3\">and and</span> on public clouds. Service state is no longer a binary up or down metric. It must be able to measure degradation in quality of service. To successfully manage modern services, IT organizations must define performance and availability monitoring metrics for a service that accurately reflect both the quality of service (outputs) and its complete set of dependencies (inputs).</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em;\">With Vistara, IT administrators can now define a composite service that integrates internally-hosted and externally-procured elements and services. IT teams can create customized definitions of availability, performance, and responsiveness so that metrics are defined in a way that fits the hybrid IT model. </span><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"78040dff-41dc-4190-9caa-c25f79b1eb5f\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"b3428997-f815-4021-aafa-0c515468a840\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"13b48d56-d368-4fe2-8bb6-d249b136583c\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"0a8c8045-fa0b-4d3b-bdeb-d72383a5026d\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"e5689a85-f6ae-4f39-9f95-fb1a90f80a53\">Vistara</span></span></span></span></span> also enables custom monitoring metrics for multi-component applications and services. You can define IT services that depend on physical and virtual elements from your private cloud, public cloud, and on-premise infrastructure and then create availability metrics for the core service, standby elements, failover elements, and redundant components.</p>\r\n<p>As IT organizations define complex services, service monitoring must match the growing sophistication and complexity of the elements they are using. <span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"1cf2d94b-0074-4651-927c-077ecfb8165d\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"52d5752d-a82d-44e7-a185-2a773f8d495b\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"1a400045-f0b5-467a-8b87-a33e7a10cf9a\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"d10bc287-2938-464a-957a-854d003e5868\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"561f4ff0-fd3a-41c4-84d9-3d73bcbafda5\">Vistara</span></span></span></span></span> makes it easy to define a service that depends on other IT elements and services, create custom metrics for service health and availability, and <span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"d7be18b4-40e9-4713-83c4-cbd9c6b15656\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"b75c86e9-af9a-46f2-9cdd-4c643804fca6\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"9c53ba52-3347-44bf-af32-a73a853ddc5a\">easily</span></span></span> represent metrics graphically. IT teams can bring up a custom dashboard with measurements of service availability and service health that automatically populate on setting up that service. With Vistara, IT administrators integrate service monitoring across multiple infrastructures and receive visibility across the entire enterprise, regardless of how the services were cobbled together and regardless of where they’re hosted.</p>\r\n<p>To learn more, <a href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/vistara-3-1\">watch our recent webinar on delivering unified IT operations</a>, which includes a brief demonstration of Vistara and its service monitoring capabilities. You can also view the slides from the webinar below.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"d7ebf343-cf46-42d9-a2b7-aa6c610d0519\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"aa20423f-8f88-4487-8e4d-fcbe00c2a99b\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"d3b9b26f-2aca-4743-8399-3d6e1412d2fb\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"4f54d915-6128-40b2-9e66-e059cf6cb119\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"c05f813f-ad89-4f6b-81f5-202c42077cf9\">Vistara</span></span></span></span></span> 3.1: Delivering Unified IT Operations: Presentation Slides</strong></p>\r\n<p><iframe style=\"border: 1px solid #CCC; border-width: 1px 1px 0; margin-bottom: 5px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"http://www.slideshare.net/slideshow/embed_code/31982975?rel=0\" height=\"356\" width=\"427\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\"><strong> <a title=\"Vistara 3.1 - Delivering Unified IT Operations\" href=\"https://www.slideshare.net/vistara/vistara-31-delivering-unified-it-operations\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"307b20be-4f6b-4d11-8886-8b27c5316f58\"><span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"de973109-1503-40c9-ae1b-2857b61b1e3f\">Vistara</span></span> 3.1 - Delivering Unified IT Operations</a> </strong> from <strong><a href=\"http://www.slideshare.net/vistara\" target=\"_blank\">Vistara</a></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em;\">Learn More!</strong></div>\r\n<p>To learn more about how Vistara can help your organization realize the full benefit of service monitoring for modern IT operations management, visit the <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/resources/demos/\">Vistara <span class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\" id=\"ecbc52ce-737c-4649-8efb-7710f4ced1b7\">demonstrations</span></a> page or request a <a href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/vistara-contact-us\">live demo</a> today!</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Image Source: Wikipedia</span></div>','Service Monitoring for Modern IT Operations','','publish','open','open','','service-monitoring-modern-it-operations','','','2014-09-19 04:44:36','2014-09-19 04:44:36','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=1371',0,'post','',0),(1373,1,'2014-03-22 12:39:51','2014-03-22 12:39:51','','','','inherit','open','open','','blog-post-service-monitoring-for-modern-it-operations','','','2014-03-22 12:39:51','2014-03-22 12:39:51','',1371,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Blog-Post-Service-Monitoring-for-Modern-IT-Operations.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1378,1,'2014-03-24 07:58:45','2014-03-24 07:58:45','','','','inherit','open','open','','datacorp-logo','','','2014-03-24 07:58:45','2014-03-24 07:58:45','',1371,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/datacorp-logo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1381,1,'2014-03-24 08:16:20','2014-03-24 08:16:20','[download id=\"1443\"]','About Us','','publish','open','open','','about-us','','','2014-03-24 17:15:36','2014-03-24 17:15:36','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=1381',0,'page','',0),(1383,1,'2014-03-24 09:52:11','2014-03-24 09:52:11','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\"><div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div></section>\r\n<section id=\"news-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"page-banner\"><div class=\"container\">\r\n<h1>Company News</h1></div>\r\n</div></section>\r\n<section class=\"section\"><div id=\"news-page\" class=\"container static-content new-news\"><div class=\"press-left\"><div class=\"row\"><h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"https://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-awsreinvent/\">Vistara to Demonstrate Modern IT Operations Management Platform at AWS re:Invent 2016</a></h2><p>SAN JOSE, CA–(Marketwired – Nov 22, 2016) - SAN JOSE, CA–(Marketwired – Nov 22, 2016) – Vistara will showcase its IT operations management platform at AWS re:Invent 2016. The SaaS-based system enables enterprise IT operations teams to scale, optimize and take full advantage of modern cloud services. Thousands of customers with hybrid cloud infrastructures already use Vistara to obtain the flexibility of public clouds, without sacrificing operational integrity. Vistara will be in booth #112.<br /> <span class=\"date\">November 22, 2016 // <a href=\"https://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-awsreinvent/\">Learn more...</a></span></p></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"https://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-soc2-type2/\">Vistara Prioritizes Data Protection with Successful SOC 2 Type 2 Audit</a></h2><p>SAN JOSE, CA--(Marketwired - Nov 1, 2016) - Vistara, a leading SaaS platform for IT operations management, announces it has successfully completed a Service Organization Control (SOC) 2 Type 2 audit. The independent audit confirms that Vistara\'s information security practices, policies and operations meet the SOC 2 Type 2 standards for availability, confidentiality and integrity.<br /> <span class=\"date\">November 1, 2016 // <a href=\"https://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-soc2-type2/\">Learn more...</a></span></p></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-most-promising-aws-solution-providers/\">CIOReview Selects Vistara as One of 20 Most Promising AWS Solution Providers in 2015</a></h2><p>FREMONT, Calif. — CIOReview has chosen Vistara for its list of 20 Most Promising AWS Solution Providers. The selection was based on the evaluation of Vistara’s ability to let an organization connect its public and private cloud resources to construct a complete picture of critical applications using service maps. Vistara manages IT services in a single framework whether the applications are built with dynamic cloud resources or in a hybrid environment. <br /> <span class=\"date\">September 30, 2015 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-most-promising-aws-solution-providers/\">Learn more...</a></span></p></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-recognized-crn-emerging-vendor/\">Vistara Recognized By CRN As A 2015 Emerging Vendor</a></h2><p>San Jose, CA — Vistara, the SaaS-based command center for IT operations management, announced today it has been named to The Channel Company’s exclusive 2015 CRN® Emerging Vendors List. The annual list features up-and-coming technology vendors that have introduced innovative new products, creating opportunities for channel partners in North America to create high-margin, cutting-edge solutions for their customers. The vendors recognized this year have demonstrated a commitment to developing new technologies to meet growing market demands. <br /> <span class=\"date\">July 22, 2015 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-recognized-crn-emerging-vendor/\">Learn more...</a></span></p></div>\r\n<div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-wins-2014-crn-tech-innovator-award/\">Vistara Wins 2014 CRN Tech Innovator Award</a></h2><p>San Jose, CA — Vistara, the only SaaS based lifecycle management solution for IT operations, announced today it has been named one of the industry’s leading tech innovators by CRN. The annual Tech Innovator Awards recognize the companies and products that have used innovation to advance technology, increase productivity, and reduce cost and complexity in ways that provide value to the channel. Vistara Lifecycle Management took top honors in the Managed Services category. <br /> <span class=\"date\">November 18, 2014 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-wins-2014-crn-tech-innovator-award/\">Learn more...</a></span></p></div>\r\n<div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-wins-vspex-valuable-player-award-emc-world-2014/\">Vistara Wins VSPEX Most Valuable Player Award at EMC World 2014</a></h2><p>Las Vegas, NV — Vistara, innovator of a comprehensive SaaS solution for modern IT operations, today announced that it has been awarded the 2014 EMC® Technology Connect VSPEX MVP Award. Vistara delivers a best-in-class unified management solution for VSPEX® technology that provides advanced features over the native tools available. Vistara is one of only three EMC Technology Connect partners across the globe to have been recognized as a Most Valuable Player as part of the inaugural 2014 Technology Connect awards.<br /> <span class=\"date\">May 7, 2014 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-wins-vspex-valuable-player-award-emc-world-2014/\">Learn more...</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-named-gartner-cool-vendor-in-it-operations-management/\">Vistara Named a “Cool Vendor” by Gartner, Inc.</a></h2><p>San Jose, CA — Vistara, innovator of a comprehensive SaaS solution for modern IT operations, today announced it has been included in Gartner, Inc.’s 2014 report, “Cool Vendors in IT Operations, 2014.” “We are delighted to be recognized as a Gartner ‘Cool Vendor’ in IT Operations,” said Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer for Vistara. “We feel being named Gartner Cool Vendor validates our belief that the market is ready for a single platform IT operations lifecycle management solution that comes in an easily consumable SaaS delivery model, and can be managed in a unified console across heterogeneous and cloud environments.”<br /> <span class=\"date\">Apr. 21, 2014 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-named-gartner-cool-vendor-in-it-operations-management/\">Learn more...</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/netskope-selects-vistara-devops-modern-it-operations-management/\">Netskope Selects Vistara for Modern IT Operations Management</a></h2><p>San Jose, CA — Vistara today announced that cloud app analytics and policy leader <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/netskope-selects-vistara-devops-modern-it-operations-management/\">Netskope has selected Vistara for Modern IT Operations Management and DevOps enablement</a>. “We chose Vistara primarily because it enables us to successfully adopt a DevOps model that has led to gains in operational efficiencies and bolstered our competitive advantage,\" said Rob Cameron, Principal Software Engineer at Netskope. “By providing us with a unified view of our entire IT operations, Vistara enables our DevOps team to monitor and manage all of our physical and virtual infrastructure through a single pane of glass without having to log in to multiple systems or use expensive VPN infrastructure.”<br /> <span class=\"date\">Dec. 19, 2013 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/netskope-selects-vistara-devops-modern-it-operations-management/\">Learn more...</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.prweb.com/releases/2013/11/prweb11306743.htm\">Computer Design and Integration (CDI LLC) Forms Strategic Partnership with Vistara</a></h2><p>Teterboro, NJ — Computer Design and Integration (CDI LLC) today announced an <a href=\"http://www.prweb.com/releases/2013/11/prweb11306743.htm\">elite strategic partnership with Vistara</a>, a cloud-delivered service for unified IT operations management. As one of a small number of authorized delivery partners, CDI will fulfill a marketplace need for more comprehensive IT lifecycle management. With this, customers will be able to view and manage their entire distributed IT infrastructure within a single user interface.<br /> <span class=\"date\">Nov. 19, 2013 // \r\n<a href=\"http://www.channelbuzz.ca/2013/09/vistara-extends-lifeline-packettrap-users-7836/\">Read the article ...</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-offers-dell-packettrap-customers-it-platform-upgrade/\">Vistara Offers Dell packetTrap Customers IT Platform Upgrade</a></h2><p>San Jose, Calif. — Vistara today announced <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-offers-dell-packettrap-customers-it-platform-upgrade/\" target=\"_blank\">a limited time promotion for enterprises, solution providers and managed services providers with active Dell packetTrap</a> network monitoring tool licenses. Available now until Dec. 31, 2013, the new swap-out incentive program offers users a more advanced and comprehensive monitoring and management solution from Vistara, the leader in modern IT operations management. Under the terms of the promotion, eligible packetTrap users who sign a 15-month contract with Vistara will receive the first three months of service at no charge<br /> <span class=\"date\">Sept. 25, 2013 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-offers-dell-packettrap-customers-it-platform-upgrade/\">Learn more…</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"https://blog.vistarait.com/vistara-30-hybrid-it-cloud-service-management\">Introducing Vistara 3.0: Hybrid IT Service Management for the Cloud</a></h2><p>San Jose, Calif. — Vistara today announced the <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/blog/vistara-30-hybrid-it-cloud-service-management/\">release of Vistara 3.0, featuring new support for hybrid IT service management spanning the private and public cloud,</a> service topology mapping, custom IT operations dashboards, management of enterprise applications including Microsoft Active Directory, Exchange, SQLServer, Internet Information Server, and MySQL, and asset management. Customers can use Vistara 3.0\'s support for hybrid IT service management to launch new services more quickly and cost-effectively while ensuring high scalability and availability.<br /> <span class=\"date\">August 5, 2013 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/blog/vistara-30-hybrid-it-cloud-service-management/\">Learn more ...</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"https://blog.vistarait.com/vistara-itop-supports-vnxe-unified-storage-platform\">EMC Labs Validates Vistara ITOP for VNXe Unified Storage</a></h2><p>LAS VEGAS — <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">Vistara</a> today announced that <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/blog/vistara-itop-supports-vnxe-unified-storage-platform/\">EMC Labs has now validated that you can leverage Vistara ITOP to provision and manage your VNXe unified storage platforms</a>. This validation continues Vistara ITOP\'s strong support for EMC® VSPEX™ Proven Infrastructure solutions.<br /> <span class=\"date\">May 8, 2013 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/blog/vistara-itop-supports-vnxe-unified-storage-platform/\">Learn more ...</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/brocade-vdx-emc-vnx-vspex-validation-vistara-itop/\">Vistara Extends Support for EMC’s VSPEX™ Proven Infrastructure with Validation from Brocade</a></h2><p>LAS VEGAS — <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">Vistara</a> today announced that <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/brocade-vdx-emc-vnx-vspex-validation-vistara-itop/\">Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP), its SaaS-based IT management as a service solution, has been successfully tested and validated by Brocade for use with Brocade® VDX® switches</a>. The validation further extends Vistara’s support for the EMC® VSPEX™ Proven Infrastructure.<br /> <span class=\"date\">May 8, 2013 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/brocade-vdx-emc-vnx-vspex-validation-vistara-itop/\"> Learn more ...</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-emerging-cloud-service-management-vendor/\">Vistara Recognized as an Emerging Cloud Service Management Vendor by Enterprise Strategy Group</a></h2><p>San Jose, Calif. — Vistara today announced that it has been <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-emerging-cloud-service-management-vendor/\">recognized by Enterprise Strategy Group (ESG) as an emerging cloud service management vendor in the firm\'s March 2013 market summary report on <em>Cloud Service Management Software</em></a>. The report acknowledges the Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP) for its ability to remotely manage and federate on-premise private cloud and public cloud operations from a single enterprise command center.<br /> <span class=\"date\">April 11, 2013 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-emerging-cloud-service-management-vendor/\">Learn more ...</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/ingram-micro-cloud-marketplace-offers-vistara-itop/\">Vistara ITOP Now Offered within the Ingram Micro Cloud Marketplace</a></h2><p>Phoenix, Ariz. — Vistara today announced that <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/ingram-micro-cloud-marketplace-offers-vistara-itop/\" target=\"_blank\"> Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP), its SaaS-based, IT management as a service solution, is now available to channel partners in the U.S. and Canada via the Ingram Micro Cloud Marketplace</a> (<a href=\"http://www.ingrammicrocloud.com/\" target=\"_blank\">www.<wbr />ingrammicrocloud.com</a>), a transactional, online marketplace where solution providers and MSPs can shop, procure, provision and obtain invoices for their cloud services directly from Ingram Micro.<br /> <span class=\"date\">April 9, 2013 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/ingram-micro-cloud-marketplace-offers-vistara-itop/\" target=\"_blank\"> Learn more ...</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/emc-vspex-vnx-validation-vistara-itop-3/\">Vistara Announces First SaaS-Based Cloud Management Solution Validated by EMC Labs</a></h2><p>San Jose, Calif. — Vistara today announced that <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/emc-vspex-vnx-validation-vistara-itop-3/\" target=\"_blank\">Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP), its cloud management solution, has been successfully tested and validated as part of an EMC® VSPEX™ Proven Infrastructure solution</a>. Customers can now leverage Vistara ITOP to provision and manage their VSPEX solution and VNX® unified storage platforms. The achievement marks Vistara ITOP as the first VSPEX Labs validated SaaS IT management solution.<br /> <span class=\"date\">March 12, 2013 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/emc-vspex-vnx-validation-vistara-itop-3/\">Learn more...</a></span></p></div><div class=\"release-wrap\"><h2 class=\"name\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/press-release-cloud-operations-solution-customer-adoption/\">Vistara Announces Growing Customer Adoption for Cloud Operations Solution</a></h2><p>San Jose, Calif. – <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/press-release-cloud-operations-solution-customer-adoption/\">Vistara announced today that its Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP) solution is now the cloud operations solution of choice</a> for more than 1,100 companies. Valued by customers for its ease of use and rich functionality, Vistara ITOP enables faster adoption of cloud-based solutions and hybrid IT environments by integrating the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds, public clouds and IT tools.<br /> <span class=\"date\">Feb. 25, 2013 // <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/press-release-cloud-operations-solution-customer-adoption/\">Learn more ...</a></span></p></div></div></div><div class=\"press-right\"><div class=\"widget-wrap\"><h3>Share this page</h3><div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div></div><div class=\"widget-wrap\"><h3>Related links</h3><div class=\"widget-inner\"><p>Vistara Lifecycle Management Solution Brief [<a href=\"https://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Vistara-Solution-Brief.pdf\">PDF</a>]</p><p>Vistara Product Demo [<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xhd9L5U4GUQ\">Video</a>]</p></div></div><div class=\"widget-wrap\"><h3>Media Contact</h3><div class=\"widget-inner\"><p><strong>Kevin Wolf </strong><br /> (650) 327-1641<br /> kevin@tgprllc.com</p></div></div><p><a class=\"btn btn-large\" href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/vistara-contact-us\">Schedule a Demo</a></p></div></div></section>','News','','publish','open','open','','news','','','2016-11-23 04:51:11','2016-11-23 04:51:11','',670,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=1383',0,'page','',0),(1391,1,'2014-03-24 10:41:42','2014-03-24 10:41:42','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div>\r\n</section><section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-center\">Netskope Selects Vistara for Modern IT Operations Management</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><i>Cloud app analytics and policy leader leverages Vistara to unify management of on-premise and cloud-based infrastructure for global IT operations</i></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p><b>San Jose, Calif., Dec. 18, 2013 </b>– <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">Vistara</a>, innovator of a comprehensive SaaS solution for modern IT operations, today announced it is the end-to-end operational management solution for Netskope’s global on-premise and cloud-based IT infrastructure. A leader in cloud app analytics and policy management, <a href=\"http://www.netskope.com\" target=\"_blank\">Netskope</a> selected Vistara to enable modern IT operations management and DevOps methodology.</p>\r\n<p>Vistara is currently being used by enterprises of all sizes to unify the monitoring and management of physical and virtual infrastructure, legacy monitoring tools, public clouds, and private clouds into a single, modern IT operations solution. Vistara offers an easy, secure and measurable way for IT professionals to monitor and manage their infrastructure remotely.</p>\r\n<p>“We chose Vistara primarily because it enables us to successfully adopt a DevOps model that has led to gains in operational efficiencies and bolstered our competitive advantage. Vistara has made it much easier for engineers who are not operations specialists to monitor and manage both on-premise and cloud-based infrastructure elements,” says Rob Cameron, Principal Software Engineer at Netskope. “By providing us with a unified view of our entire IT operations, Vistara enables our DevOps team to monitor and manage all of our physical and virtual infrastructure through a single pane of glass without having to log in to multiple systems or use expensive VPN infrastructure.”</p>\r\n<p>The nature of Netskope’s business makes it imperative that the company maintain maximum security for safeguarding sensitive customer information in the cloud. “We rely on Vistara for the unified alert management it provides, detecting issues long before they affect the end-user, as well as the secure integration across multiple monitoring tools for notification, escalation and resolution,” continues Cameron. “Furthermore, we can manage the stringent compliance requirements that are imposed when working with our customer’s confidential financial information through Vistara audit management which provides administrator session recordings with audit trails, logs, and reporting of all user activity for compliance to third-party auditors.”</p>\r\n<p>Netskope also uses Vistara to monitor capacity utilization. This helps ensure the timely provisioning of additional capacity as needed, and enhance the quality of software updates by providing visibility to development teams on issues affecting the production environment.</p>\r\n<p>Vistara announced that Rob Cameron will be presenting the first of Vistara’s “IT Visionaries” live webinars on “Modern IT Operations Management for Cloud Solutions,” on Tuesday, January 14th at 11 a.m. PT. Cameron will discuss Netskope’s industry-leading approach to DevOps and modern IT operations management. Watch Cameron’s <a href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/webinar-modern-it-operations\">on-demand webinar</a> and read the Netskope case study at <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Netskope-Case-Study-2014.pdf\">http://www.vistarait.com/netskope-modern-it-operations-case-study/</a>.</p>\r\n<p>“Vistara is the only comprehensive IT operations management as service solution in the market today, and it provides everything IT organizations need to implement modern IT operations management,” said Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer for Vistara. “We are proud to be working with Netskope to transform the management of its global IT operations. By leveraging our modern IT operations management platform to securely monitor and manage their physical and virtual infrastructure, Netskope is reaping the benefits that come from being the first-to-know whenever an infrastructure element is accessed or changed, as well as being able to detect and resolve any issues that arise automatically.”</p>\r\n<p>To learn more about Vistara’s IT platform visit<a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\"> http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Follow Vistara at<a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/blog/\"> http://www.vistarait.com/blog/</a>; on Twitter at<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/VistaraIT\"> @VistaraIT</a>; and on Facebook at<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\"> facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Vistara</strong>\r\nVistara provides a comprehensive SaaS solution for modern IT operations that is currently used by over 1000 customers. Vistara automatically discovers a customer’s entire distributed IT infrastructure and enables customers to unify IT operations management, manage public and private clouds, and deliver self-service IT. Headquartered in San Jose, Calif., Vistara sells directly and through our network of leading distributors and value added resellers. Vistara’s technology partners include some of the largest software and hardware vendors worldwide. To learn more about Vistara, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Netskope</strong>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.netskope.com\">Netskope</a> is the cloud app analytics and policy company. Only Netskope eliminates the catch-22 between being agile and being secure and compliant by providing complete visibility and enforcing sophisticated policies in cloud apps. Netskope performs deep analytics and lets decision-makers create policies in a few clicks that protect corporate data and optimize cloud app usage in real-time and at scale. With Netskope, people get their favorite cloud apps and the business can move fast, with confidence.</p>\r\n<p>Netskope is headquartered in Los Altos, California. Visit Netskope at <a href=\"http://www.netskope.com\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.netskope.com</a> and follow Netskope on Twitter <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Netskope\">@Netskope</a>.</p>\r\n<p>All other trademarks are the property of their respective owners.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n<strong>Kevin Wolf</strong>\r\n<p>(650) 327-1641<br>\r\nkevin@tgprllc.com</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Netskope Selects Vistara for Modern IT Operations Management','','publish','open','open','','netskope-selects-vistara-devops-modern-it-operations-management','','','2016-09-30 04:51:57','2016-09-30 04:51:57','',1383,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=1391',0,'page','',0),(1395,1,'2014-03-24 10:46:52','2014-03-24 10:46:52','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div>\r\n</section><section class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-center\">Vistara Offers Dell packetTrap Customers IT Platform Upgrade</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><i>Limited Time Promotion Offers packetTrap Customers Upgrade from End-of-Lifed packetTrap to Vistara’s Modern IT Operations Management</i></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p><b>San Jose, Calif., Sept. 25, 2013 </b>– <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">Vistara</a> today announced a limited time promotion for enterprises, solution providers and managed services providers with active Dell packetTrap network monitoring tool licenses.</p>\r\n<p>Available now until Dec. 31, 2013, the new swap-out incentive program offers users a more advanced and comprehensive monitoring and management solution from Vistara, the leader in modern IT operations management. Under the terms of the promotion, eligible packetTrap users who sign a 15-month contract with Vistara will receive the first three months of service at no charge.</p>\r\n<p>Vistara is a comprehensive SaaS solution that unifies monitoring and management of physical infrastructure, mobile devices, legacy monitoring tools, virtual infrastructure, public clouds, and private clouds into a single, modern IT operations platform. Designed for enterprise IT departments and managed service providers, Vistara offers an easy, secure and measurable way for IT professionals to provision, monitor and manage their infrastructure remotely.</p>\r\n<p>“When Dell packetTrap customers migrate to Vistara, they are getting much more than a network monitoring solution – they are upgrading to an IT operations platform that will help them do more while at the same time giving them a more effective way to unify and operate their IT infrastructure,” says Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer for Vistara. “We built Vistara to simplify the operations management of modern enterprise IT infrastructure. With Vistara, organizations are able to prevent problems, be the first to know when problems occur, and keep a closer watch on the overall health of their IT infrastructure.”</p>\r\n<p>To learn more about Vistara’s IT platform upgrade for packetTrap customers, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/packettrap-upgrade-vistara-modern-it-operations-management/\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">http://www.vistarait.com/packetTrap</span></a> For more information, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Follow Vistara at <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/blog/\">http://www.vistarait.com/blog/</a> on Twitter at<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/VistaraIT\">@VistaraIT</a> and on Facebook at <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\">facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>.</p>\r\n<p><b>About Vistara</b></p>\r\n<p>Vistara provides a comprehensive SaaS solution for modern IT operations that is currently used by over 1100 customers. Vistara automatically discovers a customer’s entire distributed IT infrastructure and enables customers to unify IT operations management, manage public and private clouds, and deliver self-service IT. Headquartered in San Jose, Calif., Vistara sells directly and through our network of leading distributors and value added resellers. Vistara’s technology partners include some of the largest software and hardware vendors worldwide. To learn more about Vistara, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Kevin Wolf</strong>\r\n<p>(650) 327-1641<br>\r\nkevin@tgprllc.com</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Vistara Offers Dell packetTrap Customers IT Platform Upgrade','','publish','open','open','','vistara-offers-dell-packettrap-customers-it-platform-upgrade','','','2016-09-30 05:10:30','2016-09-30 05:10:30','',1383,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=1395',0,'page','',0),(1402,1,'2014-03-24 10:59:59','2014-03-24 10:59:59','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\"><div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\"]</div></section><section class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-center\">Vistara Announces Growing Customer Adoption for Cloud Operations Solution</h1>\r\n<p><i>More than 1,100 Enterprises are Now Using Vistara’s SaaS Platform to Enable a Service Approach to IT Operations and Cloud Infrastructure</i></p>\r\n<p><strong>San Jose, Calif., Feb. 25, 2013</strong> &ndash; <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">Vistara</a> announced today that its Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP) solution is now the cloud operations solution of choice for more than 1,100 companies. Valued by customers for its ease of use and rich functionality, Vistara ITOP enables faster adoption of cloud-based solutions and hybrid IT environments by integrating the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds, public clouds and IT tools.</p>\r\n<p>“The Vistara platform is one of the core components of our company’s Cloud Management as a Service (CMaaS) offering,” said Ron Dupler, CEO of<a href=\"http://www.greenpages.com/\"> GreenPages Technology Solutions</a>, a $130 million national IT consulting and integration organization headquartered in Kittery, Maine. “It provides unparalleled visibility into, and control of, physical, virtual and cloud resources through a single pane of glass&mdash;crucial for organizations to effectively manage modern hybrid cloud environments.”</p>\r\n<p>Offering an intuitive interface and single pane of glass dashboard, Vistara ITOP has proven its ability to simplify IT automation and performance reporting, saving companies operational expenses and technical resources. It also seamlessly integrates with leading cloud hosting services, hardware devices, virtualized solutions, applications and operating systems, making it ideal for blended IT environments.</p>\r\n<p>Vistara ITOP lets administrators view and manage their entire distributed IT infrastructure within a single user interface, making it perfect for enterprises with multiple branch offices, remote service providers, and distributed data centers. It is the only broad solution of its kind to be offered as a comprehensive SaaS solution, meaning Vistara ITOP automatically updates and manages itself so IT professionals can focus on developing and delivering applications instead of managing them.</p>\r\n<p>“Enterprises today need to innovate quickly and leverage massively distributed human and cloud infrastructure resources. They need to ensure rapid time to resolution regardless of where a problem occurs,” says Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer of Vistara. “Modern IT organizations have to do things differently to maintain technical and business advantage, and a SaaS approach to comprehensive IT services in hybrid environments helps them do this.”</p>\r\n<p>Gartner Inc. forecasts that cloud IT operations management will have a compound average growth rate of 41.3% from 2011-2016.<sup>[1]</sup> A recent Gartner report authored by Thomas Bittman further confirms the growing market demand stating, “Client interest in building the capability to leverage external cloud services interoperably with a private and/or on-premises cloud (in a hybrid mode) is growing.<sup>[2]</sup> ”</p>\r\n<p>“The global marketplace is seeing the tip of the iceberg when it comes to demand for an interoperable cloud management solution that can remotely and accurately manage everything from the core to the edge of the network,” concludes Kunaparaju.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/product/unified-it-operations-management/\">Vistara ITOP</a> is now available as a service in the U.S. and Canada. For more information, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>. Follow Vistara at <a href=\"http://blog.vistarait.com/\">http://blog.vistarait.com/</a>; on Twitter at <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/VistaraIT\">@VistaraIT</a>; and on Facebook at <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\">facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>. See Vistara ITOP at Booths 209 and 208 at VMware Partner Exchange in Las Vegas from February 25-28, 2013.</p>\r\n<p><sup>[1]</sup> Ed Anderson, et al. “Forecast Overview: Public Cloud Services, Worldwide, 2011-2016, 4Q12 Update.” Gartner, Inc. February 2013.</p>\r\n<p><sup>[2]</sup> Bittman, Thomas J. “Top Five Trends for Private Cloud Computing.” Gartner Inc. 14 February 2012.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Vistara</strong><br>\r\nVistara is the leading provider of SaaS-based cloud operations software. It unifies islands of infrastructure, clouds, and the people who support them into a single manageable IT operation. Its flagship product, Vistara ITOP, &nbsp;is a world-class cloud operations solution that federates the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds and public clouds. Used by more than 1100 companies, Vistara ITOP enables IT professionals to view and manage their entire distributed IT infrastructure from within a single pane of glass and enables a service provider approach to IT operations. To learn more about Vistara ITOP, visit<a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\"> http://www.vistarait.com</a>. Follow VistaraIT on Twitter at<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/VistaraIT\"> @VistaraIT</a>, read the company blog at<a href=\"http://blog.vistarait.com/\"> http://blog.VistaraIT.com</a>, and engage with VistaraIT on Facebook at<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\"> http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>.</p>\r\n</div></div></div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Kevin Wolf</strong>\r\n<p>(650) 327-1641<br>\r\nkevin@tgprllc.com</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n','Vistara Announces Growing Customer Adoption for Cloud Operations Solution','','publish','open','open','','press-release-cloud-operations-solution-customer-adoption','','','2016-09-30 04:57:22','2016-09-30 04:57:22','',1383,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=1402',0,'page','',0),(1407,1,'2014-03-24 11:09:04','2014-03-24 11:09:04','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\"><div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\"]</div></section><section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-center\">Vistara Announces First SaaS-Based&nbsp;Cloud Management Solution Validated by EMC Labs</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><i>Successful Testing and Validation of Vistara ITOP within EMC’s VSPEX Labs Provides an Easier Way for Customers and Channel Partners to Provision and Manage Integrated Infrastructure and Unified Storage Solutions</i></p>\r\n<p><b>San Jose, Calif., March 12, 2013</b>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">Vistara</a>&nbsp;today announced that Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP), its SaaS-based cloud management solution, has been successfully tested and validated as part of an EMC&reg;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.emc.com/platform/virtualizing-information-infrastructure/vspex.htm\">VSPEX&trade;</a>&nbsp;Proven Infrastructure solution. Customers can now leverage Vistara ITOP to provision and manage their VSPEX solution and VNX&reg; unified storage platforms. The achievement marks Vistara ITOP as the first VSPEX Labs validated SaaS IT management solution.</p>\r\n<p>“Vistara ITOP’s new support for VSPEX Proven Infrastructure and VNX unified storage platforms shows our depth of commitment as a partner of EMC,” says Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer of Vistara. “The intensive testing and validation we completed with EMC assures our mutual customers will be able to experience the simplicity and ease-of-use that comes from leveraging Vistara ITOP’s single pane of glass view to manage their EMC solution alongside all of their other distributed IT infrastructure.”</p>\r\n<p>The cloud operations solution of choice for more than 1,100 companies, Vistara ITOP simplifies the adoption and management of cloud-based solutions and hybrid IT environments by federating the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds, public clouds and IT tools into a single dashboard. &nbsp;Customers can now use Vistara ITOP to quickly and easily provision their VSPEX converged infrastructure solution and VNX storage as a private cloud. Unlike other converged infrastructure management solutions, Vistara ITOP is available as a SaaS solution, meaning Vistara ITOP automatically updates and manages itself so IT professionals can focus on developing and delivering applications instead of managing them.</p>\r\n<p>“We are pleased to work with Vistara to deploy EMC VSPEX converged infrastructure and VNX unified storage solutions alongside the Vistara ITOP provisioning and cloud management solution,” said Parmeet Chaddha, vice president solutions, EMC. “By working together, our mutual customers and channel partners now have another great option to deploy an EMC solution with enriched management and orchestration capabilities.”</p>\r\n<p>“As technology continues to converge and adoption of cloud soars, the need for a comprehensive IT lifecycle management solution is undeniable,” concludes Kunaparaju. “We’re ensuring that Vistara ITOP easily scales to support everything from the core to the edge of the network.”</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/product/unified-it-operations-management/\">Vistara ITOP</a>&nbsp;is now available as software as a service. For more information, visit&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>. Follow Vistara at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://blog.vistarait.com/blog/\">http://www.vistarait.com/blog/</a>; on Twitter at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/VistaraIT\">@VistaraIT</a>; and on Facebook at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\">facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>.</p>\r\n<p><b>About Vistara</b></p>\r\n<p>Vistara is the leading provider of SaaS-based cloud operations software. It unifies islands of infrastructure, clouds, and the people who support them into a single manageable IT operation. Its flagship product, Vistara ITOP, is a world-class cloud operations solution that federates the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds and public clouds. Used by more than 1100 companies, Vistara ITOP enables IT professionals to view and manage their entire distributed IT infrastructure from within a single pane of glass and enables a service provider approach to IT operations. To learn more about Vistara ITOP, visit&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n</div></div></div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Kevin Wolf</strong>\r\n<p>(650) 327-1641<br>\r\nkevin@tgprllc.com</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n','Vistara Announces First SaaS-Based Cloud Management Solution Validated by EMC Labs','','publish','open','open','','emc-vspex-vnx-validation-vistara-itop-3','','','2016-09-30 04:58:34','2016-09-30 04:58:34','',1383,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=1407',0,'page','',0),(1412,1,'2014-03-24 11:17:31','2014-03-24 11:17:31','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\"><div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\"]</div></section><section class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-center\">Vistara ITOP Now Offered within the Ingram Micro Cloud Marketplace</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><i>SaaS Innovator Inks Strategic Distribution Alliance with the World’s Largest Technology Distributor Ingram Micro</i></p>\r\n<p><strong>Phoenix, Ariz., April 9, 2013 &mdash;&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">Vistara</a> today announced that Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP), its SaaS-based, IT management as a service solution, is now available to channel partners in the U.S. and Canada via the Ingram Micro Cloud Marketplace (<a href=\"http://www.ingrammicrocloud.com/\">www.ingrammicrocloud.com</a>), a transactional, online marketplace where solution providers and MSPs can shop, procure, provision and obtain invoices for their cloud services directly from Ingram Micro.</p>\r\n<p>The new North America distribution agreement was announced by Vistara and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ingrammicro.com/\">Ingram Micro Inc.</a> (NYSE: IM) at the distributor’s fourth annual Cloud Summit themed “All Sky. No Limit.” taking place this week in Phoenix, Ariz. Under the terms of the agreement, Ingram Micro’s cloud sales team will actively market and sell Vistara’s SaaS-based IT management as a service solution to its growing base of cloud-focused solutions providers who are offering managed services, as well as professional IT services.</p>\r\n<p>Designed as an enterprise command center for technology professionals, Vistara ITOP is a cost-effective and comprehensive SaaS solution that makes it possible for value added resellers (VARs), system integrators and solution providers to effectively and remotely manage hybrid IT environments from a single dashboard. To date more than 1,100 businesses are remotely managed by managed service providers using Vistara.</p>\r\n<p>“Vistara is an ideal cloud-based management platform for full-service solution providers who want to scale their services business and manage costs while maximizing profitability and service levels,” says Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer for Vistara. “This new relationship with Ingram Micro quickly expands our sales reach.”</p>\r\n<p>“Cloud services is an explosively growing marketplace that offers great opportunity for channel partners &ndash; especially those who are well positioned to remotely manage the entire IT ecosystem with ease and efficiency,” says Renee Bergeron, vice president of managed services and cloud computing, Ingram Micro Services Division, North America. “We’re pleased to offer Vistara as part of our growing cloud services portfolio and bring to market a solution that is proven to help managed service providers effectively scale their IT services business and manage on premise solutions, as well hybrid and cloud solutions.”</p>\r\n<p>Ingram Micro channel partners who are interested in learning more about Vistara should contact the Ingram Micro Cloud services team at (800) 705-7057, option 1, or email <a href=\"mailto:cloud.management@ingrammicro.com\">cloud.management@ingrammicro.com</a>.&nbsp;.</p>\r\n<p>For more information, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>. Follow Vistara at <a href=\"http://blog.vistarait.com/blog/\">http://www.vistarait.com/blog/</a>; on Twitter at <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/VistaraIT\">@VistaraIT</a>; and on Facebook at <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\">facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Ingram Micro Cloud<br>\r\n</strong>Ingram Micro Cloud (<a href=\"http://www.ingrammicrocloud.com\">www.ingrammicrocloud.com</a>) provides channel partners access to hundreds of business, strategy, marketing, technical and sales resources including the Ingram Micro Cloud Marketplace, a transactional, online marketplace where solution providers can shop, procure, provision and obtain invoices for their cloud services directly from Ingram Micro.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About&nbsp;Ingram Micro Inc.</strong><br>\r\nIngram Micro&nbsp;is the world’s largest wholesale technology distributor and a global leader in IT supply-chain, mobile device lifecycle services and logistics solutions. As a vital link in the technology value chain,&nbsp;Ingram Micro&nbsp;creates sales and profitability opportunities for vendors and resellers through unique marketing programs, outsourced logistics and mobile solutions, technical support, financial services and product aggregation and distribution. The company is the only global broad-based IT distributor, serving approximately 160 countries on six continents with the world’s most comprehensive portfolio of IT products and services. Visit&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ingrammicro.com/\">www.ingrammicro.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Vistara</strong><br>\r\nVistara is the leading provider of IT management as a service software. It unifies infrastructure, clouds and people into a single manageable IT operation. Its flagship product, Vistara ITOP, is a world-class IT management as a service solution that federates the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds and public clouds. Used by more than 1100 companies, Vistara ITOP enables IT professionals to view and manage their entire distributed IT infrastructure from within a single pane of glass and enables a service provider approach to IT operations. To learn more about Vistara ITOP, visit&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Kevin Wolf</strong>\r\n<p>(650) 327-1641<br>\r\nkevin@tgprllc.com</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n','Vistara ITOP Now Offered within the Ingram Micro Cloud Marketplace','','publish','open','open','','ingram-micro-cloud-marketplace-offers-vistara-itop','','','2016-09-30 04:59:30','2016-09-30 04:59:30','',1383,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=1412',0,'page','',0),(1417,1,'2014-03-24 11:24:31','2014-03-24 11:24:31','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\"><div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\"]</div></section><section class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-center\">Vistara Recognized as an Emerging Cloud Service Management Vendor by Enterprise Strategy Group</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><i>Vistara ITOP Supports the Ten Key Components of Cloud Service Management Required for IT Organizations to Successfully Become Cloud Services Providers (CSPs)</i></p>\r\n<p><strong>San Jose, CA&ndash;(Marketwired, Apr 11, 2013) &mdash;&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">Vistara</a> today announced that&nbsp;it has been recognized by <a href=\"http://www.esg-global.com/\">Enterprise Strategy Group (ESG)</a> as an emerging cloud service management vendor in the firm’s March 2013 market summary report on <em>Cloud Service Management Software</em>. The report acknowledges the Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP) for its ability to remotely manage and federate on-premise private cloud and public cloud operations from a single enterprise command center.</p>\r\n<p>“Vistara is pleased to be included in ESG’s market summary report on Cloud Service Management Software and sees an increasing demand for cloud-based IT management as a service software,” says Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer for Vistara. “This recognition by ESG is proof positive of our growing industry leadership and the innovative technology that defines our Vistara ITOP solution.”</p>\r\n<p>As part of its new report, ESG asserts that IT organizations must deliver upon the National Institute of Standards and Technology’s (NIST) five tenets of cloud computing &mdash; on-demand/self-service, broad network access, resource pooling, rapid elasticity and measured service &mdash; as well as meet ten core components to successfully transform themselves into CSPs. These ten core components include automation, Single Sign-On (SSO), Governance, Risk and Compliance (GRC), service management, service catalogs, Change Management Databases (CMDB), service desk, orchestration, chargeback and federation.</p>\r\n<p>“Vistara ITOP is uniquely positioned to deliver on all ten of the key components of cloud service management outlined within ESG’s report,” continues Kunaparaju. “Another critical differentiator is the simplicity and ease-of-use CSPs experience when using Vistara’s single pane of glass view to remotely manage and support hybrid IT environments.”</p>\r\n<p>Vistara ITOP is the only converged management solution that is also available as a SaaS solution. As such, the platform easily scales and simplifies the adoption and management of cloud-based solutions and hybrid IT environments by federating the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds, public clouds and IT tools.</p>\r\n<p>“Vistara is an emerging vendor we will continue to watch as part of our market research on the cloud service management marketplace,” said Wayne Pauley, Senior Analyst, ESG. “The breadth and depth of the Vistara ITOP solution is impressive, and the fact it’s offered as a SaaS solution and meets the criteria CSPs need to be successful certainly commands attention.”</p>\r\n<p>For an overview of ESG’s March 2013 market summary report on Cloud Service Management Software, visit Wayne Pauley’s <a href=\"http://www.esg-global.com/blogs/implementing-private-and-hybrid-clouds-with-cloud-service-management/\">Video Blog: Implementing Private and Hybrid Clouds with Cloud Service Management</a>.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/product/unified-it-operations-management/\">Vistara ITOP</a> is now available as software as a service. For more information, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com.\">http://www.vistarait.com.</a>&nbsp;Follow Vistara at <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/blog/\">http://www.vistarait.com/blog/</a> on Twitter at <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/VistaraIT\">@VistaraIT</a> and on Facebook at <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\">facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Vistara</strong><br>\r\nVistara is the leading provider of IT management as a service software. It unifies infrastructure, clouds and people into a single manageable IT operation. Its flagship product, Vistara ITOP, is a world-class IT management as a service solution that federates the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds and public clouds. Used by more than 1100 companies, Vistara ITOP enables IT professionals to view and manage their entire distributed IT infrastructure from within a single pane of glass and enables a service provider approach to IT operations. To learn more about Vistara ITOP, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Kevin Wolf</strong>\r\n<p>(650) 327-1641<br>\r\nkevin@tgprllc.com</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n','Vistara Recognized as an Emerging Cloud Service Management Vendor by Enterprise Strategy Group','','publish','open','open','','vistara-emerging-cloud-service-management-vendor','','','2016-09-30 05:00:56','2016-09-30 05:00:56','',1383,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=1417',0,'page','',0),(1422,1,'2014-03-24 11:30:43','2014-03-24 11:30:43','<section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-center\">Vistara Extends Support for EMC’s VSPEX&trade; Proven Infrastructure with Validation from Brocade</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><i>IT Professionals can now use Vistara ITOP to Provision and Manage Brocade&reg; VDX&reg; Ethernet Fabric Switches alongside EMC&reg; VNX&reg; Unified Storage Solutions</i></p>\r\n<p><strong></strong><strong>LAS VEGAS, May 8, 2013 &mdash; </strong><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">Vistara</a> today announced that Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP), its SaaS-based IT management as a service solution, has been successfully tested and validated by Brocade for use with Brocade&reg; VDX&reg; switches. The validation further extends Vistara’s support for the EMC&reg; VSPEX&trade; Proven Infrastructure.</p>\r\n<p>“Vistara ITOP is pleased to expand the breadth and depth of its support for industry-leading components of EMC VSPEX Proven Infrastructure solutions, which now includes Brocade VDX switches,” says Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer for Vistara. “The successful testing and validation of Vistara ITOP by Brocade ensures that our mutual customers will benefit from the simplicity and ease-of-use that comes from using our SaaS-based IT management as a service solution to provision and manage their entire distributed IT infrastructure.”</p>\r\n<p>Vistara ITOP simplifies the adoption and management of cloud-based solutions and hybrid IT environments by federating the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds, public clouds and IT tools into a single dashboard. Available as a SaaS solution, Vistara ITOP automatically updates and manages itself so IT professionals can focus on developing and delivering applications instead of managing them.</p>\r\n<p>“The Vistara ITOP platform seamlessly interfaces with the automated configuration capabilities of Brocade VDX switches to further advance the value proposition we deliver with EMC VSPEX cloud and virtualization solutions,” said Jason Nolet, vice president of the Data Center Networking Group at Brocade. “The Vistara infrastructure management and orchestration capabilities exceeded our testing and validation requirements and enable our channel partners’ customers to better provision and manage network and storage resources.”</p>\r\n<p>Earlier this year, Vistara announced support for <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/emc-vspex-vnx-validation-vistara-itop-3/\">EMC’s VSPEX Proven Infrastructure and VNX unified storage solutions</a> “The successful testing and validation of the Vistara ITOP platform combined with Brocade’s VDX switches gives customers transforming IT greater ease in provisioning and managing their VNX storage infrastructure solutions,” said Parmeet Chaddha, vice president solutions, EMC.</p>\r\n<p>For more information, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com.\">http://www.vistarait.com.</a>&nbsp;Follow Vistara at <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/blog/\">http://www.vistarait.com/blog/</a> on Twitter at <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/VistaraIT\">@VistaraIT</a> and on Facebook at <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\">facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>.</p>\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 18px; height: 25px;\">About Brocade</div>\r\n<p>Brocade (NASDAQ: BRCD) networking solutions help the world’s leading organizations transition smoothly to a world where applications and information reside anywhere. (<a href=\"http://ctt.marketwire.com/?release=1000143&amp;id=2797240&amp;type=1&amp;url=http%3a%2f%2fwww.brocade.com%2f\">www.brocade.com</a>)</p>\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 18px; height: 25px;\">About Vistara</div>\r\n<p>Vistara is the leading provider of IT management as a service software. It unifies infrastructure, clouds and people into a single manageable IT operation. Its flagship product, Vistara ITOP, is a world-class IT management as a service solution that federates the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds and public clouds. Used by more than 1100 companies, Vistara ITOP enables IT professionals to view and manage their entire distributed IT infrastructure from within a single pane of glass and enables a service provider approach to IT operations. To learn more about Vistara ITOP, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">http://www.vistarait.com</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"># # #</p>\r\n<p><em>Brocade and VDX are registered trademarks of Brocade Communications Systems. EMC, VSPEX and VNX are registered trademarks or trademarks of EMC Corporation in the United States and other countries. All other trademarks are the property of their respective owners.</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Kevin Wolf</strong>\r\n<p>(650) 327-1641<br>\r\nkevin@tgprllc.com</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n','Vistara Extends Support for EMC’s VSPEX™ Proven Infrastructure with Validation from Brocade','','publish','open','open','','brocade-vdx-emc-vnx-vspex-validation-vi