les enterprise IT and service providers to see their entire IT infrastructure, control across elements, automate management, and optimize availability, performance and capacity to drive unified IT operations. Headquartered in San Jose, California, Vistara sells directly and through our network of leading distributors and value added resellers. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Product Manager (Enterprise Software, Hyderabad, Telangana)','','publish','open','open','','product-manager-vistara-operations-management-platform-enterprise-software-hyderabad-india','','','2014-11-06 12:25:49','2014-11-06 12:25:49','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=2160',0,'page','',0),(2163,1,'2014-04-02 08:18:51','2014-04-02 08:18:51','<section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<h1>Interactive Designer (Enterprise Software, Hyderabad, India)</h1>\r\n<p><span id=\"a1f2bfcd-c905-4b87-8472-3710bdbeca7e\" class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\"><span id=\"c678eb77-3188-4c1f-9848-5667b8ccfab9\" class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\"><span id=\"191c3c1b-c9aa-49db-9d0c-d0eee08a7e2f\" class=\"GINGER_SOFTWARE_mark\">Vistara</span></span></span> is looking for an Interactive Designer who will work on the creation and implementation of visual designs across our website, social media, email campaigns, events, and more.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong>This position is an opportunity to grow your career by working at a disruptive technology company, developing your skills in enterprise software marketing, and accelerating our growth.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Location:&nbsp;</strong>Hyderabad, India</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reports to:</strong>&nbsp;Senior Director of Marketing</p>\r\n<p>Interested? Email your resume to&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:marketing-jobs@vistarait.com\">marketing-jobs@vistarait.com</a>.&nbsp;Principals only.</p>\r\n<h2>Responsibilities</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Create highly engaging and compelling