es)</h1>\r\n<p>Vistara 3.1 includes advanced features for unified IT operations management including automated reporting functionality that can be scheduled on a user defined or on-demand basis, support for access controls at a granular level for enhanced security, dashboards for Microsoft applications like SharePoint and Lync, and monitoring of popular open source databases and infrastructure.</p>\r\n<div class=\"tube20y\">\r\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"400\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/U1Cz0xfZJCw\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Vistara 3.1: Delivering Unified IT Operations (Webinar) (49 Minutes)','','publish','open','open','','vistara-3-1-delivering-unified-operations','','','2014-04-11 07:09:20','2014-04-11 07:09:20','',1307,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=2258',0,'page','',0),(2261,1,'2014-04-04 07:04:24','2014-04-04 07:04:24','','demo','','publish','open','open','','demo','','','2014-04-17 08:11:45','2014-04-17 08:11:45','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=2261',0,'page','',0),(2264,1,'2014-04-04 07:07:52','2014-04-04 07:07:52','<section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<h1>IT Operations Management As A Service (Webinar) (55 Minutes)</h1>\r\n<p>Today IT operations must be delivered as a service centrally using a supply chain of on-premise and cloud-based resources. Vistara is the only comprehensive IT operations management solution that enables enterprise IT teams to act as service provider to lines of business.</p>\r\n<div class=\"tube20y\">\r\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"400\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/bPMnxeJVexQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','  IT-Management-as-a-ServiceIT Operations Management As A Service (Webinar) (55 Minutes)','','publish','open','open','','it-operations-management-as-a-service','','','2014-04-11 07:10:50','2014-04-11 07:10:50','',1307,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=2264',0,'page','',0),(2266,1,'2014-04-04 07:10:03','2014-04-04 07:10:03','<section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<h1>Vistara 3.0: Hybrid IT Service Management for the Cloud (Webinar)</h1>\r\n<p>This 40 minute webinar discusses the new features added to Vistara 3.0. Vistara 3.0 features new support for hybrid service definition, monitoring, and management to support today’s hybrid IT operations model and the ability to customize its administrator dashboard so your team can focus on what matters most. It also supports custom escalation matrixes and the ability to manage assets over their lifecycle.</p>\r\n<div class=\"tube20y\">\r\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"400\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/6iOyyxCkzTs\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Vistara 3.0: Hybrid IT Service Management for the Cloud (Webinar)','','publish','open','open','','vistara-3-0-hybrid-it-service-management-for-the-cloud','','','2014-04-11 07:13:24','2014-04-11 07:13:24','',1307,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=2266',0,'page','',0),(2269,1,'2014-04-04 07:14:32','2014-04-04 07:14:32','<section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<h1>Hybrid IT Operations and the Hybrid Cloud (Webinar)</h1>\r\n<p>This 40 minute webinar discusses how in hybrid IT, enterprises leverage the private and public cloud and services built upon them to deliver new services. Hybrid cloud services enable enterprises to offer new IT solutions more quickly and cost effectively. Vistara is uniquely suited to support the hybrid IT model through its support for the monitoring and management of infrastructure and services on-premise and on the private and public cloud.</p>\r\n<div class=\"tube20y\">\r\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"400\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/Bbrz_GKsRkU\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Hybrid IT Operations and the Hybrid Cloud (Webinar)','','publish','open',