Vice President of Sales</p>\r\n<p>Interested? Email a resume in reverse chronological format to <a href=\"mailto:marketing-jobs@vistarait.com\">marketing-jobs@vistarait.com</a>. Principals only.</p>\r\n<h2>Responsibilities</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Work with Business Development and Marketing to drive sales and marketing strategy, planning and execution with technology and channel partners.</li>\r\n	<li>Create and execute partner specific marketing plans for increasing demand and visibility of Vistara’s SaaS solution.</li>\r\n	<li>Create new and re-purposed marketing materials for partner use, in conjunction with internal and external teams.</li>\r\n	<li>Deliver partner support for channel sales operations and customer demo engagements.</li>\r\n	<li>Coordinate partner marketing activities across sales, product management, product marketing, and executive teams.</li>\r\n	<li>Deliver partner support across different initiatives for tradeshows, webinars, website content, social media, and press releases.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Experience</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2+ years of previous work experience in partner management in marketing or sales in the enterprise technology industry.</li>\r\n	<li>Relevant work experience includes developing and implementing marketing and sales strategies in the channel sales / B2B marketing space.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong knowledge of technology and channel partner business models and sales processes.</li>\r\n	<li>Proven skills in rolling out integrated marketing programs for generating qualified sales leads.</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to write marketing materials and other business documents in American English with native-level fluency without assistance. All applicants will be required to complete an in-person writing exercise to demonstrate their writing ability.</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent analytical ability and attention to detail.</li>\r\n	<li>Demonstrated ability to manage multiple programs and priorities.</li>\r\n	<li>Passion for rapid execution and delivering quality results quickly.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong skills in using Microsoft Office suite and online collaboration solutions such as Google Docs.</li>\r\n	<li>Some flexibility in work hours to enable communication with staff and partners in US time zones.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>About Vistara</h2>\r\n<p>Vistara provides a comprehensive SaaS solution for modern IT operations that is currently used by over 1000+ customers. Vistara automatically discovers a customer’s entire distributed IT infrastructure and enables customers to unify their IT operations, manage public and private clouds, and deliver self-service IT. To learn more about Vistara, visit http://www.vistarait.com.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Partner Program Manager (Enterprise Software, Hyderabad, India)','','private','open','open','','partner-program-manager-enterprise-software-hyderabad-india','','','2014-06-13 07:33:03','2014-06-13 07:33:03','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=2304',0,'page','',0),(2324,1,'2014-04-07 11:55:43','2014-04-07 11:55:43',' ','','','publish','open','open','','2324','','','2015-04-29 11:15:20','2015-04-29 11:15:20','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=2324',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(2325,1,'2014-04-07 11:55:43','2014-04-07 11:55:43',' ','','','publish','open','open','','2325','','','2015-04-29 11:15:20','2015-04-29 11:15:20','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=2325',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(2326,1,'2014-04-07 11:55:44','2014-04-07 11:55:44',' ','','','publish','open','open','','2326','','','2015-04-29 11:15:20','2015-04-29 11:15:20','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=2326',8,'nav_menu_item','',0),(2327,1,'2014-04-07 11:55:45','2014-04-07 11:55:45',' ','','','publish','open','open','','2327','','','2015-04-29 11:15:20','2015-04-29 11:15:20','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=2327',16,'nav_menu_item','',0),(2329,1,'2014-04-07 11:55:43','2014-04-07 11:55:43',' ','','','publish','open','open','','2329','','','2015-04-29 11:15:20','2015-04-29 11:15:20','',320,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=2