ss=\"section\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n       <div class=\"heading-box\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"alignleft\">Quickly identify root cause and remediate</h2><div class=\"alignright\"><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/product/vistara-lifecycle-management/\"><img class=\"rotate\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/wheel.png\" alt=\"Back to Overview\" title=\"Back to Overview\"></a></div>\r\n          <h4>Vistara lets you analyze root cause and remediate using automation and secure remote access.</h4>\r\n       </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"section\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n      <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n        <div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n           <h3>Root Cause Analysis</h3>\r\n           <p>Vistara gives information needed to quickly apply common patterns of root cause analysis.</p>\r\n           <ul>\r\n               <li>View complete details and history of alerts and events associated to a service, group or element in one pane to quickly apply common patterns of root cause analysis</li>\r\n<li>Look at deviations from historical event behavior and configuration changes, the behavior of an element after a change, and compare key metrics between elements to understand the reason for deviation from norm</li>\r\n           </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n   <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n      <div class=\"cloudcnt-box\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/troubleshooting-cause.png\" />\r\n      </div>\r\n</div>  \r\n    <div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"section\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n      <div class=\"cloudcnt-box\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/troubleshooting-remediation.png\" />\r\n      </div>\r\n</div>\r\n      <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n        <div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n           <h3>Remediation</h3>\r\n           <p>Most remediations conditions can be quickly addressed from within Vistara itself. </p>\r\n           <ul>\r\n               <li>Define automation policies for self remediation of common issues before escalating as an incident </li>\r\n              <li>Common remediating actions can be performed from within Vistara with just a few commands and at scale, applying remediating action across multiple devices</li>\r\n              <li>Remediating actions can be audited and managed for a proper change\r\n</li>\r\n           </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n     \r\n    <div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"section\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n        <div class=\"cloudcnt-box\">\r\n           <h3>Secure Remote Access</h3>\r\n           <ul>\r\n               <li>Launch remote consoles to analyze the problem with real time information, change the configurations or remediate issues</li>\r\n               <li>Interact with multiple consoles from single UI, run SCP file transfer and broadcast single command across multiple consoles</li>\r\n                <li>View recorded console sessions for change management, compliance and training</li>\r\n           </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n      <div class=\"cloudcnt-box\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/troubleshooting-Remote .png\" />\r\n<a class=\"ghost-button-rounded-cornersxsm aligncenter\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Data Sheet_Console Recordings_2015.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download Datasheet</a>      \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n     \r\n    <div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"section-green\">\r\n			<div class=\"container\">\r\n				<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n                                     <div class=\"subscribe-box\">\r\n                                          <img class=\"sub-icon\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Question-icon-80x80.png\" alt=\"