ationships</li>\r\n	<li>Integrated reporting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-3051 shadow-img alignnone\" alt=\"fas-5\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/fas-5.jpg\" width=\"207\" height=\"80\" /></p>\r\n<p>Managing secure multi-tenancy requires implementing policies not only on the FAS storage, but also on the server, network, and hypervisors. With Vistara you have one tool that can manage and audit the whole SMT implementation. Vistara gives you the big picture with lifecycle components including:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"background: none;\">\r\n	<li>Agentless management</li>\r\n	<li>Secure session recording</li>\r\n	<li>Change audit</li>\r\n	<li>Application correlation</li>\r\n	<li>Guest host to ESX Correlation</li>\r\n	<li>Network mapping</li>\r\n	<li>Server mapping</li>\r\n	<li>Automated reporting</li>\r\n	<li>Automated incident ticketing</li>\r\n	<li>Role based access control</li>\r\n	<li>Time based access control</li>\r\n	<li>Business facing, automated service catalog</li>\r\n	<li>Federated cloud management</li>\r\n	<li>Change approval</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"gettingStarted\"></div>\r\n<h2><a style=\"font-size: 13px;\" href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/vistara-contact-us\">Contact us</a><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\"> to request a demo and see for yourself!</span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','NetApp FAS','','publish','open','open','','netapp-fas','','','2014-04-14 09:51:07','2014-04-14 09:51:07','',93,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=3046',0,'page','',0),(3050,1,'2014-04-14 07:10:08','2014-04-14 07:10:08','','','','inherit','open','open','','fas-4','','','2014-04-14 07:10:08','2014-04-14 07:10:08','',3046,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/fas-4.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(3051,1,'2014-04-14 07:10:39','2014-04-14 07:10:39','','','','inherit','open','open','','fas-5','','','2014-04-14 07:10:39','2014-04-14 07:10:39','',3046,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/fas-5.jpg',0,'attachment','image/j