ent','image/jpeg',0),(3137,1,'2014-04-17 01:14:20','2014-04-17 01:14:20','','mail','','inherit','open','open','','mail','','','2014-04-17 01:14:20','2014-04-17 01:14:20','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/mail.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(3138,1,'2014-04-17 01:14:20','2014-04-17 01:14:20','','pinterest','','inherit','open','open','','pinterest','','','2014-04-17 01:14:20','2014-04-17 01:14:20','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/pinterest.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(3139,1,'2014-04-17 01:14:20','2014-04-17 01:14:20','','twitter','','inherit','open','open','','twitter','','','2014-04-17 01:14:20','2014-04-17 01:14:20','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/twitter.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(3140,1,'2014-04-17 01:23:19','2014-04-17 01:23:19','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\"><div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\"]</div></section>\r\n<section class=\"section\">\r\n    <div class=\"container static-content press-container\">\r\n    	<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n       		<div class=\"row\">\r\n         		<h2>Press Releases</h2>\r\n            	<h1>Vistara Announces Growing Customer Adoption for Cloud Operations Solution</h1>\r\n           	<p class=\"headline-text\"><i>More than 1,100 Enterprises are Now Using Vistara’s SaaS Platform to Enable a Service Approach to IT Operations and Cloud Infrastructure</i></p>\r\n             	<p class=\"release-date\"><span>San Jose, Calif., Feb. 25, 2013 &ndash;</span></p>\r\n              	<p><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\">Vistara</a> announced today that its Vistara IT Operations Platform (ITOP) solution is now the cloud operations solution of choice for more than 1,100 companies. Valued by customers for its ease of use and rich functionality, Vistara ITOP enables faster adoption of cloud-based solutions and hybrid IT environments by integrating the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds, public clouds and IT tools.</p>\r\n             	<p>“The Vistara platform is one of the core components of our company’s Cloud Management as a Service (CMaaS) offering,” said Ron Dupler, CEO of<a href=\"http://www.greenpages.com/\"> GreenPages Technology Solutions</a>, a $130 million national IT consulting and integration organization headquartered in Kittery, Maine. “It provides unparalleled visibility into, and control of, physical, virtual and cloud resources through a single pane of glass&mdash;crucial for organizations to effectively manage modern hybrid cloud environments.”</p>\r\n             	<p>Offering an intuitive interface and single pane of glass dashboard, Vistara ITOP has proven its ability to simplify IT automation and performance reporting, saving companies operational expenses and technical resources. It also seamlessly integrates with leading cloud hosting services, hardware devices, virtualized solutions, applications and operating systems, making it ideal for blended IT environments.</p>\r\n              	<p>Vistara ITOP lets administrators view and manage their entire distributed IT infrastructure within a single user interface, making it perfect for enterprises with multiple branch offices, remote service providers, and distributed data centers. It is the only broad solution of its kind to be offered as a comprehensive SaaS solution, meaning Vistara ITOP automatically updates and manages itself so IT professionals can focus on developing and delivering applications instead of managing them.</p>\r\n               	<p>“Enterprises today need to innovate quickly and leverage massively distributed human and cloud infrastructure resources. They need to ensure rapid time to resolution regardless of where a problem occurs,” says Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer of Vistara. “Modern IT organizations have to do things differently to maintain technical and business advantage, and a SaaS approach to comprehensive IT services in hybrid environments helps them do this.”</p>\r\n               	<p>Gartner Inc. forecasts that cloud IT operations management will have a compound average growth rate of 41.3% from 2011-2016.<sup>[1]</sup> A recent Gartner report authored by Thomas Bittman further confirms the growing market demand stating, “Client interest in building the capability to leverage external cloud services interoperably with a private and/or on-premises cloud (in a hybrid mode) is growing.<sup>[2]</sup> ”</p>\r\n               	<p>“The global marketplace is seeing the tip of the iceberg when it comes to demand for an interoperable cloud management solution that can remotely and accurately manage everything from the core to the edge of the network,” concludes Kunaparaju.</p>\r\n              	<p><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/product/unified-it-operations-management/\">Vistara ITOP</a> is now available as a service in the U.S. and Canada. For more information, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>. Follow Vistara at <a href=\"http://blog.vistarait.com/\">http://blog.vistarait.com/</a>; on Twitter at <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/VistaraIT\">@VistaraIT</a>; and on Facebook at <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\">facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>. See Vistara ITOP at Booths 209 and 208 at VMware Partner Exchange in Las Vegas from February 25-28, 2013.</p>\r\n             	<p><sup>[1]</sup> Ed Anderson, et al. “Forecast Overview: Public Cloud Services, Worldwide, 2011-2016, 4Q12 Update.” Gartner, Inc. February 2013.</p>\r\n               	<p><sup>[2]</sup> Bittman, Thomas J. “Top Five Trends for Private Cloud Computing.” Gartner Inc. 14 February 2012.</p>\r\n            	<p><strong>About Vistara</strong><br>\r\n                Vistara is the leading provider of SaaS-based cloud operations software. It unifies islands of infrastructure, clouds, and the people who support them into a single manageable IT operation. Its flagship product, Vistara ITOP, &nbsp;is a world-class cloud operations solution that federates the remote management of on-premise clouds, virtual private clouds and public clouds. Used by more than 1100 companies, Vistara ITOP enables IT professionals to view and manage their entire distributed IT infrastructure from within a single pane of glass and enables a service provider approach to IT operations. To learn more about Vistara ITOP, visit<a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/\"> http://www.vistarait.com</a>. Follow VistaraIT on Twitter at<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/VistaraIT\"> @VistaraIT</a>, read the company blog at<a href=\"http://blog.vistarait.com/\"> http://blog.VistaraIT.com</a>, and engage with VistaraIT on Facebook at<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\"> http://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>.</p>\r\n               	<p>Press contact:<br>\r\n                Suzanne Collier<br>\r\n               	WhiteFox Marketing<br>\r\n               	<a href=\"mailto:suzanne@whitefoxpr.com\">suzanne@whitefoxpr.com</a><br>\r\n              	(714) 572-1498</p>\r\n         	</div>\r\n   	</div>\r\n     	<div class=\"press-right alignright\">\r\n       		<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n          		<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n                        <div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n                </div>\r\n           	<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n       		     <h3>Related links</h3>\r\n              	     <div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n              	          <p>Netskope’s Rob Cameron discusses how Vistara enabled Netskope’s DevOps model [<a href=\"#\">Video</a>]</p>\r\n                          <p>Netskope Case Study [<a href=\"#\">PDF</a>]</p>\r\n              	     </div>\r\n      	 	</div>\r\n                <div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n          	     <h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n            	     <div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n                          <p><strong>Suzanne Collier</strong><br />(714) 572-1498<br />suzanne@whitefoxpr.com</p>\r\n                     </div>\r\n           	