','',0),(3258,1,'2014-04-21 00:00:46','2014-04-21 00:00:46','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div>\r\n</section><section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content new-news\" id=\"news-page\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<h1>Press Release</h1>\r\n<div class=\"release-wrap\">\r\n<h2 class=\"name\">Vistara Named a “Cool Vendor” by Gartner, Inc.</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>IT operations management innovator recognized for being Innovative, Impactful and Intriguing</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><b>SAN JOSE, Calif., April 21, 2014 </b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Vistara, innovator of a comprehensive SaaS solution for modern IT operations, today announced it has been included in Gartner, Inc.’s 2014 report, “Cool Vendors in IT Operations, 2014.”</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>“We are delighted to be recognized as a Gartner ‘Cool Vendor’ in IT Operations,” said Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer for Vistara. “We feel being named Gartner Cool Vendor validates our belief that the market is ready for a single platform IT operations lifecycle management solution that comes in an easily consumable SaaS delivery model, and can be managed in a unified console across heterogeneous and cloud environments.”</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Gartner\'s annual Cool Vendors report recognizes emerging vendors who are delivering solutions that challenge long-held assumptions and significant investments in traditional IT. These companies are transforming the way businesses operate and consumers engage with technology.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>According to the “Cool Vendors in IT Operations, 2014” report, “Tools for effective decision making can improve the infrastructure and operations (I&amp;O) team\'s ability to allocate resources to the right types of activities. The Cool Vendors featured in this year\'s research demonstrate new ways to improve automation of ITOM tasks, as well as a focus on merged views for monitoring and management.”</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Additionally, Gartner says, “IT operations leaders should review up-and-coming ITOM products to find new approaches to control costs, improve service and manage risk.”</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>“Vistara provides the single pane of glass across the distributed physical, virtual and cloud-based IT infrastructure that our enterprise IT customers are looking for,” continues Kunaparaju. “We will continue to strive towards our vision to revolutionize IT operations by delivering world-class modern IT into the enterprise.”</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To learn more about Vistara’s IT platform visit <a title=\"Vistara Home Page\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Follow Vistara at <a title=\"Vistara Blog\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/blog/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vistarait.com/blog/</a>; on Twitter at <a title=\"Twitter @VistaraIT\" href=\"https://twitter.com/VistaraIT\" target=\"_blank\">@VistaraIT</a>; and on Facebook at <a title=\"Vistara at Facebook\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\" target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Vistara</strong>\r\nVistara provides a comprehensive SaaS solution for modern IT operations that is currently used by over 1000 customers. Headquartered in San Jose, Calif., Vistara enables enterprise IT and service providers to see their entire IT infrastructure, control across elements, automate management, and optimize availability, performance and capacity to drive unified IT operations. To learn more about Vistara, visit <a title=\"Vistara Home Page\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Disclaimer</strong>\r\nGartner does not endorse any vendor, product or service depicted in its research publications, and does not advise technology users to select only those vendors with the highest ratings. Gartner research publications consist of the opinions of Gartner\'s research organization and should not be construed as statements of fact. Gartner disclaims all warranties, expressed or implied, with respect to this research, including any warranties of merchantability or fitness for a particular purpose.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>[<a title=\"Gartner Cool Vendors in IT Operations, 2014\" href=\"http://www.gartner.com/document/2706920\" target=\"_blank\">1</a>] Gartner \"Cool Vendors in IT Operations, 2014\" by Jeffrey M. Brooks, et al. April 11, 2014</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"># # #</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>All other trademarks are the property of their respective owners.</em></p></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Related links</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n<p>Research Report: <a href=\"http://www.gartner.com/document/2706920\" target=\"_blank\">Gartner Cool Vendors in IT Operations, 2014</a> by Jeffrey M. Brooks, et al. April 11, 2014</p>\r\n<p>Gartner Blog: <a href=\"http://blogs.gartner.com/jonah-kowall/2014/04/15/contribution-cool-vendors-in-it-operations-management/\" target=\"_blank\">Jonah Kowall - Cool Vendors in IT Operations Management</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n<strong>Kevin Wolf</strong>\r\n<p>(650) 327-1641<br>\r\nkevin@tgprllc.com</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Vistara Named Gartner Cool Vendor in IT Operations Management','','publish','open','open','','vistara-named-gartner-cool-vendor-in-it-operations-management','','','2016-09-28 12:40:05','2016-09-28 12:40:05','',1383,'http://www.vistarait.com/?