ttp://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/sap_solutionmanager.png\"/><!--<span>SAP Solution Manager is an Application Lifecycle Management (ALM). The Vistara integration allows Vistara to accept alerts from SAP Solution Manager.</span>--></div> </li>\r\n<li><div class=\"box200\"><img width=\"140\" height=\"75\" alt=\"Sensu\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/sensu_tech_int.png\"/><!--<span>Sensu is an open-source monitoring framework that allows organizations to compose comprehensive monitoring and telemetry solutions. The Vistara integration allows Vistara to accept alerts from Sensu.</span>--></div> </li>\r\n<li><div class=\"box200\"><img width=\"140\" height=\"75\" alt=\"Solarwinds\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/solarwinds_tech_int.png\"/><!--<span>SolarWinds provides IT management software, including network, database and system management, IT security and IT help desk. The Vistara integration allows Vistara to accept alerts from SolarWinds.</span>--></div> </li>\r\n<li><div class=\"box200\"><img width=\"140\" height=\"75\" alt=\"System Center\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Microsoft_System_Center.png\"/><!--<span>Microsoft System Center Operations Manager (SCOM) is a data center management system for operating systems and hypervisors. The Vistara integration allows Vistara to accept alerts from SCOM.</span>--></div> </li>\r\n<li><div class=\"box200\"><img width=\"140\" height=\"75\" alt=\"Zabbix\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/zabbix_tech_int.png\"/><!--<span>Zabbix is an open source monitoring solution for network servers, devices, services and other IT resources. The Vistara integration allows Vistara to accept alerts from Zabbix.</span>--></div> </li>\r\n<li><div class=\"box200\"><img width=\"140\" height=\"75\" alt=\"Zenoss\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/zenoss.png\"/></div> </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"section-co