ope performs deep analytics and lets decision-makers create policies to protect corporate data as well as optimize cloud app usage quickly, easily and at scale. </p>\r\n<p class=\"text-right\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Netskope-Case-Study-2014.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/pdf.png\"> Read the Case Study</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<div id=\"unified-operations\"><section id=\"see-box\" class=\"section-white\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box1\">\r\n <iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/SOT0QyD73k0?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe><br><br>\r\n<h2>“Over the years, we have seen the things that don’t work and Vistara didn’t have those things. We no longer have to go through thousands of command prompt sessions to figure out what the issue is. Vistara helps us detect and resolve issues automatically.”</h2>\r\n<h5><strong>Rob Cameron </strong><br>\r\nPrincipal DevOps Engineer, Netskope</h5>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"custompost-titlebox2\">\r\n<p class=\"pull-left\"><img class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"Hybrid Cloud\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Webinar-icon.png\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" /></p>\r\n<h4>Watch our on-demand webinar with Rob Cameron on <a href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/webinar-modern-it-operations\">\"Modern IT Operations Management for Cloud Solutions\"</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"control-box\" class=\"section-colored\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\r\n<h2>The Challenge</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Scale infrastructure rapidly for enhancing operational efficiencies and bolstering competitive advantage</li>\r\n        <li>Help engineering and operations collaborate seamlessly on product development and deployment</li>\r\n        <li>Enable operations team members around the world to work together for keeping its solution running 24/7</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box\"> \r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\r\n<h2>The Requirement</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n\r\nNetskope wanted an innovative solution that could meet their unique challenges for IT operations management:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Alert management for faster problem resolution and responsive support</li>\r\n    <li>Unified monitoring for managing on-premise, virtual, and cloud infrastructure</li>\r\n    <li>Robust monitoring templates for meeting enterprise-specific policies and needs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\r\n<h2>Business Benefits</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\nVistara Lifecycle Management enabled Netskope to unify management of on-premise and cloud-based infrastructure and helped Netskope grow by focusing on things that are important and eliminate the things that are tedious (alerting, management, monitoring, templates, server on-boarding, virtual machine setup and decommissioning old instances).\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Single pane of glass view of the IT environment across physical, virtual, private cloud and public cloud infrastructure</li>\r\n    <li>Customizable monitoring templates that deliver best practices for managing all of Netskope’s customer networks</li>\r\n    <li>Secure remote access for ensuring that each engineer accesses only those elements they are authorized to view and manage</li>\r\n    <li>Patch and configuration management for ensuring that all of Netskope’s servers stay up to date with the latest patch releases</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"casestudy-page\" class=\"section-white\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><a class=\"cs-button\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Netskope-Case-Study-2014.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/pdf-g.png\"> Read the Case Study <i class=\"fa fa-file-pdf-o\"></i></a>&nbsp; or &nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"cs-button\" href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/vistara-contact-us\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/demo.png\"> Request a Demo<i class=\"fa fa-file-pdf-o\"></i></a></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Case Study - Netskope','','private','open','open','','netskope','','','2015-07-24 06:09:24','2015-07-24 06:09:24','',3963,'http://www.vistarait.com/product/unified-it-operations-management-2/',0,'page','',0),(4342,36,'2014-08-22 09:49:09','2014-08-22 09:49:09','','pdf','','inherit','open','open','','pdf','','','2014-08-22 09:49:09','2014-08-22 09:49:09','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/pdf.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(4344,1,'2014-03-05 11:02:32','2014-03-05 11:02:32','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\" class=\"leafnode-nav\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div>\r\n</section><section id=\"casestudy-datacorp-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"page-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h1>Case Study - DATACORP</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section class=\"request-demo section-colored\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<h2><img class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail wp-post-image pull-left\" alt=\"Datacorp\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Datacorp.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"75\" style=\"margin-right:20px;\"/>DATACORP Transforms Its Managed Services Business with Vistara</h2>\r\n<p class=\"big-font tube10y\">\r\nData Corporation is a premier South Florida technology company that provides managed services and IT outsourcing to mid and small enterprises. DATACORP\'s expertise helps clients move high cost on-premise infrastructure to cutting edge, cost effective cloud based services such as IaaS and SaaS technology, allowing customers to focus on their core business. \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-right\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/DataCorp-Case-Study-2014.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/pdf.png\"> Read the Case Study</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<div id=\"unified-operations\"><section id=\"see-box\" class=\"section-white\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box1\">\r\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"166\" scrolling=\"no\" frameborder=\"no\" src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/164858203&amp;color=ff5500&amp;auto_play=false&amp;hide_related=false&amp;show_comments=true&amp;show_user=true&amp;show_reposts=false\"></iframe><BR>\r\n<div><p>&nbsp;</p></div>\r\n<h2>“Vistara provides greater visibility into our clients’ environment, letting us manage our clients more effectively and efficiently. With Vistara, not only has our customer satisfaction gone up, but also we are able to manage more customers and companies with the engineers that we have. Vistara has increased profitability, consistency and insight. The solution pays for itself in preventing downtime for our customers. It allows me to be a better managed service provider.”</h2>\r\n<h5><strong>Terrisa McMillan </strong><br>\r\nDirector of Consulting, DATACORP</h5>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"custompost-titlebox2\">\r\n<p class=\"pull-left\"><img class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"Hybrid Cloud\" src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Webinar-icon.png\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" /></p>\r\n<h4> Watch our on-demand webinar with Terrisa McMillan on <a href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/webinar-managed-services-business\">\"Growing Your Managed Services Business with Vistara\"</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"control-box\" class=\"section-colored\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\r\n<h2>The Challenge</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Lack of visibility into client environments to proactively prevent and address customer problems</li>\r\n        <li>Time was wasted working on basic maintenance with multiple tools for managing different technology vendor solutions across customers</li>\r\n        <li>Point tools lacked the IT operations functionality that DATACORP required to serve its customers</li>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box\"> \r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\r\n<h2>The Requirement</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\nDATACORP had specific requirements for their next IT operations management solution:\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Patch management capability</li>\r\n    <li>Proactive visibility into IT infrastructure elements</li>\r\n    <li>Discovery tool to support presales, inventory, and asset discovery</li>\r\n    <li>Flexible solution that allows for scalable customization</li>\r\n    <li>Options for managing both on-premise and virtual appliances</li>\r\n    <li>Robust and complete Reporting tools</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\r\n<h2>Business Benefits</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\nVistara Lifecycle Management was deployed in all DATACORP customer IT environments for managing functions (monitoring and alerts, patch and anti-virus management, incident management) across IT operations lifecycle management.\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Identify potential customer issues and proactively resolve problems before they impact the customer’s business</li>\r\n    <li>Do more with the resources as Vistara helps check status, alert and maintenance records in one place</li>\r\n    <li>Ability to deliver customization, proactive service, and robust reporting with Vistara has boosted DATACORP’s customer satisfaction </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"casestudy-page\" class=\"section-white\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><a class=\"cs-button\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/DataCorp-Case-Study-2014.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/pdf-g.png\"> Read the Case Study <i class=\"fa fa-file-pdf-o\"></i></a>&nbsp; or &nbsp;&nbsp;<a class=\"cs-button\" href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/vistara-contact-us\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/demo.png\"> Request a Demo<i class=\"fa fa-file-pdf-o\"></i></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Case Study - DATACORP','','private','open','open','','datacorp','','','2015-07-24 06:10:30','2015-07-24 06:10:30','',3963,'http://www.vistarait.com/company/resources/casestudy-netskope-2/',0,'page','',0),(4373,36,'2014-08-23 10:57:17','2014-08-23 10:57:17','','google_cloud_tech_int','','inherit','open','open','','google_cloud_tech_int','','','2014-08-23 10:57:17','2014-08-23 10:57:17','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/google_cloud_tech_int.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(4374,36,'2014-08-23 10:59:31','2014-08-23 10:59:31','','iis8_tech_int','','inherit','open','open','','iis8_tech_int','','','2014-08-23 10:59:31','2014-08-23 10:59:31','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/iis8_tech_int.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(4377,36,'2014-08-23 11:21:34','2014-08-23 11:21:34',''