and located in Little Falls, NJ, is a technology solutions provider whose core business is ensuring its clients’ productivity and efficiency through the appropriate use of advanced technology solutions.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-right\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Promedia-Case-Study-2014.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/pdf.png\"> Read the Case Study</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<div id=\"unified-operations\"><section id=\"see-box\" class=\"section-white\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box\">\r\n\r\n<h2>“Vistara enables us to control and optimize the infrastructure that makes sure that school districts are connected, compliant and secure. With Vistara, we can ensure performance, security, availability, and maintainability of critical infrastructure.”</h2>\r\n<h5><strong>Kevin O’Connor</strong><br>\r\nDirector of Service Delivery, Promedia</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"control-box\" class=\"section-colored\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\r\n<h2>The Challenge</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Manage complex customer infrastructure that help run applications for online testing, learning environments, and compliance with state regulations</li>\r\n        <li>Deliver visibility across all the elements that support school surveillance systems and help protect students and staff</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box\"> \r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\r\n<h2>The Solution</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\nPromedia needed an integrated IT operations lifecycle management solution that can monitor and manage customer infrastructure across heterogeneous IT environments:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Monitors all of the elements that are critical to the physical surveillance system</li>\r\n    <li>Provide service maps to notify engineers when there is an incident with any element that impacts service levels</li>\r\n     <li>Delivers full knowledge into the status of all of the elements that keep a school secure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"custompost-box\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9\">\r\n<h2>Business Benefits</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post-content\">\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Unified monitoring across the distributed infrastructure so that Promedia engineers have full knowledge into the status of all of the elements that keep the school secure</li>\r\n    <li>Proactive incident management so that alerts are automatically ticketed and engineers can control all the elements from Vistara’s single pane of glass</li>\r\n    <li>See, control, automate and optimize the physical, virtual, cloud and application elements to make sure that schools are connected, compliant and secure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"casestudy-page\" class=\"section-white\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Promedia-Case-Study-2014.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/pdf.png\"> Read the Case Study</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Case Study - Promedia','','private','open','open','','promedia','','','2014-08-28 14:40:40','2014-08-28 14:40:40','',3963,'http://www.vistarait.com/company/resources/casestudynetskope-2/',0,'page','',0),(4476,1,'2014-04-10 16:33:22','2014-04-10 16:33:22','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\"><div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div></section><section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content new-news\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<h1>Presentation: Delivering Un