<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h1>Marketing Analyst (Enterprise Software, Hyderabad, Telangana)</h1>\r\n<p>Vistara is looking for a Marketing Analyst who will create tailored prospect datasets for inside sales and marketing campaigns. The analyst will also provide structured analysis, effective metrics and executive reports to drive marketing productivity and effectiveness in a fast growing GTM environment. The candidate should be results-driven and detail-oriented, and ready to think outside the box to help marketing and sales make the best decisions to drive Vistara opportunities.</p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Department:</strong> Marketing</p>\r\n<p><strong>Title of the role:</strong> Marketing Analyst</p>\r\n<p><strong>Location:</strong> Hyderabad, Telangana</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reports to:</strong> Senior Director of Marketing</p>\r\n<p><strong>Interested?</strong> Email a resume in reverse chronological format to <mailto:marketing-jobs@vistarait.com>marketing-jobs@vistarait.com</a>. Principals only.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><h2>Responsibilities:</h2></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Perform in-depth research on companies, industries, and people as per campaign requirements using internal and external resources.</li>\r\n	<li>Work with sales and marketing teams to deliver prospect information from varied data sources.</li>\r\n	<li>Grow our prospect database by initiating and overseeing data capture, append, and data entry projects.</li>\r\n	<li>Drive and execute marketing database strategy – analyzing gaps in our data, executing ongoing account and contact acquisition, ensuring the highest level of data quality, and measuring database health.</li>\r\n	<li>Collaborate with marketing and sales to understand when a lead is \"sales - ready\", and manage lead scoring and threshold campaigns to successfully track and handover leads.</li>\r\n	<li>Maintaining reports and dashboards that drive analysis resulting in maximizing the productivity of process and value of campaigns.</li>\r\n	<li>Actively monitoring marketing contribution to new opportunity pipeline via dashboards and reporting.</li>\r\n	<li>Aiding in the development, management, and maintenance of lead scoring and lead nurturing programs.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><h2>Requirements:</h2></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2 plus years of previous experience in marketing operations at a B2B technology company highly desired. The right candidate may have a consulting or market research background.</li>\r\n	<li>Analytical approach to problem solving; comfort with both qualitative and quantitative analysis.</li>\r\n	<li>Experience with marketing automation platforms, ideally HubSpot. Familiarity with Salesforce.com highly desired.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong working knowledge of Microsoft Excel.</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent native English written and verbal communication skills.</li>\r\n	<li>Some flexibility in work hours to enable communication with staff and partners in US time zones.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b>Who We Are: </b>Vistara provides a comprehensive SaaS solution that delivers IT operations lifecycle management spanning physical, virtual, cloud and application elements. Vistara enables enterprise IT and service providers to see their entire IT infrastructure, control across elements, automate management, and optimize availability, performance and capacity to drive unified IT operations. Headquartered in San Jose, California, Vistara sells directly and through our network of leading distributors and value added resellers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Marketing Analyst (Enterprise Software, Hyderabad, Telangana)','','publish','open','open','','marketing-analyst-enterprise-software-hyderabad-telangana','','','2014-11-06 12:27:01','2014-11-06 12:27:01','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=4938',0,'page','',0),(4954,36,'2014-10-31 12:43:56','2014-10-31 12:43:56','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section id=\"career-pageb\">\r\n<div class=\"page-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h1>Careers</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"company-page\">\r\n<section id=\"aboutus-box\" class=\"section-white\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n\r\n<h2>Disrupt the Future of IT Ops!</h2>\r\n<p>Vistara is on a mission to revolutionize IT operations to meet our customers’ modern IT needs. We are building a team of talented people who thrive in a culture of development, agility and innovation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you’re an experienced software engineer or leader with a passion to work in a fast moving, DevOps oriented culture with regular hackathons, sprint driven product development, and twice a month major releases, Vistara is the place for you. Our technology platform collects over a billion metrics using big data platforms on a daily basis and we dissect it religiously to understand how it’s working for our customers. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you’re passionate about driving Go-To-Market for an innovative SaaS solution that can change the game for customers and partners, we’re looking for exceptional sales and marketing experts to drive demand generation, build customer relationships and close opportunities. Our product is used daily by Netflix, Dolby, Toyota, and a thousand other incredible companies and on track for many more. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vistara is headquartered in San Jose, California with additional offices in Hyderabad and Bhimavaram, India. We offer competitive salaries, comprehensive benefits, and the opportunity to work with enthusiastic, hard-working people who get things done.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If this sounds like the place for you, apply to our open positions below. If you don\'t see a position that fits you, let us know how you think you can contribute to Vistara by writing us at <a href=\"mailto:careers@vistarait.com?Subject=Apply to Vistara\">careers@vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section id=\"careers-box\" class=\"section-colored\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h2>PRODUCT MANAGEMENT</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/about-us/careers/product-manager-it-operations-management-platform-enterprise-software-hyderabad-india/\">Product Manager (Hyderabad, Telangana)</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/user-experience-designer-enterprise-software-hyderabad-telangana/\">User Experience Designer (Hyderabad, Telangana)</a></p>\r\n<div><p>&nbsp;</p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n</section>','Careers - PRODUCT MANAGEMENT','','private','open','open','','careers-product-management','','','2016-07-18 14:17:10','2016-07-18 14:17:10','',670,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=4954',0,'page','',0),(4973,36,'2014-10-31 12:53:20','2014-10-31 12:53:20',' ','','','publish','open','open','','4973','','','2014-12-08 06:22:22','2014-12-08 06:22:22','',670,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=4973',10,'nav_menu_item','',0),(4985,31,'2014-10-31 17:55:29','2014-10-31 17:55:29','<img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Shadow-IT-Blog-Post1.jpg\" alt=\"Cloud Drives Down Shadow IT\" width=\"258\" height=\"389\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-5062\" /><p> Two years ago, <a href=\"http://www.gartner.com/newsroom/id/1862714\" target=\"_blank\">analyst firm Gartner</a> predicted that by 2015, over 35 percent of IT spend would no longer be controlled by the IT department. Shadow IT was going to eat the CIO\'s lunch and business units would directly procure cloud solutions bypassing corporate IT teams. Summing up the prevailing consensus, <a href=\"http://blogs.gartner.com/mark_mcdonald/2012/03/22/lightening-the-depth-of-shadow-it/\" target=\"_blank\">Gartner analyst Mark P. McDonald</a>  remarked, \"Shadow IT is growing in many organizations driven by consumerized technology, mobility, the availability of cloud solutions and <i>quite frankly relatively slow cycle times within captive IT organizations.\"</i></p>  \r\n\r\n<p> However, instead of rendering IT departments irrelevant, the cloud has enabled CIOs become instrumental in selecting technology that helps employees do their job effectively. <a href=\"http://cloud.verizon.com/enterprise-cloud-report\" target=\"_blank\">Verizon\'s Enterprise Cloud 2014 report</a> confirms that IT departments are playing a crucial role in business transformation and the \"cloud is fundamentally redefining IT’s relevance to the business.\" What resulted in this transformation? According to the report: \"The best CIOs have made <b>building strong ties with the lines of business</b> a core objective. This has been helped by a general growth in the level of IT savviness and a shared focus on innovation as a differentiator.\"</p> \r\n\r\n<p>Increasing cloud adoption has enhanced the role of IT departments in procuring technology that meets business goals, reducing implementation risks with clearly defined policies, and defining governance and standards for cloud usage. Today the business is looking at IT leaders to \"enable innovative application and product development while maintaining security.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some highlights on the waning of shadow IT from the report:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Over 80% of cloud spend is managed by the IT department. And 62% of that has the direct involvement of the CIO.</li>\r\n	<li>The CIO and their team actively own most cloud decisions, particularly when it comes to IaaS and PaaS purchases.</li>\r\n	<li>Cloud decisions are being driven by IT leaders. The IT function is playing a vital role in improving the rigor with which cloud procurement is approached.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Internal IT has  tamed the specter of shadow IT by embracing the cloud and helping business <i>“obtain the required standards of compliance, security, reliability, performance, and value for money in service delivery.”</i> Here\'s to greater innovation, quicker delivery, and more freedom with the cloud, all thanks to enterprise IT! ','Thanks To The Cloud, CIOs Are Reining In Shadow IT ','','publish','open','open','','reining-shadow-it','','','2014-11-04 11:29:12','2014-11-04 11:29:12','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=4985',0,'post','',0),(5000,36,'2014-11-03 11:20:58','2014-11-03 11:20:58','','John Tonthat-webinar','','inherit','open','open','','john-tonthat-webinar','','','2014-11-03 11:20:58','2014-11-03 11:20:58','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/John-Tonthat-webinar.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5001,36,'2014-11-03 11:21:26','2014-11-03 11:21:26','','John Tonthat-webinar','','inherit','open','open','','john-tonthat-webinar-2','','','2014-11-03 11:21:26','2014-11-03 11:21:26','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/John-Tonthat-webinar1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5003,43,'2014-11-03 12:07:05','2014-11-03 12:07:05',' ','','','publish','open','closed','','5003','','','2016-09-12 05:31:01','2016-09-12 05:31:01','',93,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5003',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5004,43,'2014-11-03 12:07:05','2014-11-03 12:07:05',' ','','','publish','open','closed','','5004','','','2016-09-12 05:31:01','2016-09-12 05:31:01','',93,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5004',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5005,43,'2014-11-03 12:07:05','2014-11-03 12:07:05',' ','','','publish','open','closed','','5005','','','2016-09-12 05:31:01','2016-09-12 05:31:01','',93,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5005',7,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5006,43,'2014-11-03 12:07:05','2014-11-03 12:07:05',' ','','','publish','open','closed','','5006','','','2016-09-12 05:31:01','2016-09-12 05:31:01','',93,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5006',8,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5007,43,'2014-11-03 12:07:05','2014-11-03 12:07:05',' ','','','publish','open','closed','','5007','','','2016-09-12 05:31:01','2016-09-12 05:31:01','',93,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5007',9,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5008,43,'2014-11-03 12:07:05','2014-11-03 12:07:05',' ','','','publish','open','closed','','5008','','','2016-09-12 05:31:01','2016-09-12 05