,'',0),(5039,43,'2014-11-03 12:20:38','2014-11-03 12:20:38',' ','','','publish','open','closed','','5039','','','2016-09-12 05:31:02','2016-09-12 05:31:02','',1160,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5039',37,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5042,43,'2014-11-03 12:27:33','2014-11-03 12:27:33','','closeBtn','','inherit','open','open','','closebtn-2','','','2014-11-03 12:27:33','2014-11-03 12:27:33','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/closeBtn1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5045,43,'2014-11-03 13:38:43','2014-11-03 13:38:43',' ','','','publish','open','closed','','5045','','','2016-09-12 05:31:01','2016-09-12 05:31:01','',320,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5045',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5046,43,'2014-11-03 13:38:43','2014-11-03 13:38:43','','Overview','','publish','open','closed','','overview-6','','','2016-09-12 05:31:01','2016-09-12 05:31:01','',320,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5046',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5050,43,'2014-11-04 05:38:23','2014-11-04 05:38:23','','Partner Resources','','publish','open','closed','','partner-resources-2','','','2016-09-12 05:31:01','2016-09-12 05:31:01','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5050',27,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5059,31,'2014-11-04 11:16:27','2014-11-04 11:16:27','','Cloud Drives Down Shadow IT','','inherit','open','open','','clouds-2','','','2014-11-04 11:17:08','2014-11-04 11:17:08','',4985,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Shadow-IT-Blog-Post.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5060,31,'2014-11-04 11:17:23','2014-11-04 11:17:23','','Cloud Drives Down Shadow IT','','inherit','open','open','','clouds-3','','','2014-11-04 11:17:38','2014-11-04 11:17:38','',4985,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Shadow-IT-Blog-Feed.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5062,31,'2014-11-04 11:24:54','2014-11-04 11:24:54','','Cloud Drives Down Shadow IT','','inherit','open','open','','cloud-computing','','','2014-11-04 11:25:13','2014-11-04 11:25:13','',4985,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Shadow-IT-Blog-Post1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5063,31,'2014-11-04 11:25:34','2014-11-04 11:25:34','','Cloud Drives Down Shadow IT','','inherit','open','open','','cloud-computing-2','','','2014-11-04 11:25:45','2014-11-04 11:25:45','',4985,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Shadow-IT-Blog-Feed1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5143,31,'2014-11-11 10:02:06','2014-11-11 10:02:06','<p> As an IT leader, if you are waiting for reasons to embrace DevOps, look no further than the recent <a href=\"http://www.rackspace.co.uk/sites/default/files/devops-automation-report.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">DevOps Adoption</a> report commissioned by Rackspace. Rackspace surveyed 700 IT decision makers and 250 employees across the United States, the United Kingdom, and Australia to understand drivers for Enterprise DevOps implementation. The research findings apply to organizations of all sizes - 45% of respondents had more than 1,000+ employees, 35% between 501 to 1,000 employees, and 20% between 251 to 500 employees.</i></p>  \r\n\r\n<p> The report confirms that enterprises are using DevOps practices as a foundation for delivering great software that exceeds customers expectations and increases business agility. According to the report: “The 700 businesses we spoke to confirm a real appetite for the kind of development and operational processes today’s digitally-focused businesses need. DevOps is <strong>really all about getting development and operations teams to work together</strong> towards common goals – delighting the end customer, delivering business value and driving business profitability.”</p> \r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/DevOps-Report.png\" alt=\"DevOps Adoption Is Accelerating\" width=\"625\" height=\"573\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-5154\" />\r\n<em  style=\"font-size:12px;\">Businesses are seeing measurable benefits by adopting DevOps, <a href=\"http://www.rackspace.com/blog/a-devops-snapshot-rackspace-survey-shows-businesses-benefits-of-devops-infographic/\" target=\"_blank\">from the DevOps Adoption Study Infographic</a></em>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are some surprising and not-so-surprising findings from the Rackspace study:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>State of Adoption</strong>. 86% of IT and business decision makers have either implemented DevOps or will roll out DevOps initiatives within the next 3 years. In line with best practices, 49% of respondents who’ve deployed DevOps have fully integrated their Dev and Ops teams while 47% have aligned DevOps with their long-term business objectives.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Release Velocity</strong>. On average, organizations are building 18 new applications and rolling out 50 upgrades for existing applications every year. It’s simply not possible to attain this level of release velocity without development and operations teams closely collaborating across the application lifecycle.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Organizational Impetus</strong>. The primary department responsible for introducing DevOps processes is the IT Operations department. 43% of DevOps rollouts were initiated by the IT Operations team and 16% by the Development team. In only 25% of organizations, CIOs were instrumental in launching DevOps initiatives.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Business Impact</strong>. Hearteningly, early adopters of DevOps have great news to share. 93% of organizations surveyed confirmed that DevOps has delivered significant benefits, with 52% mentioning increased customer satisfaction, 49% reduced IT infrastructure costs, and 44% reduction in application downtime.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Measurable Benefits</strong>. On the technical side, 57% of organizations have been able to deliver new features faster, 43% have reduced time to market, and 41% are able to respond more quickly to business needs.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>If you want your organization to deliver better software faster, embrace the growing movement of DevOps to achieve greater agility, better collaboration, and lower application failures. Start your DevOps journey now by <a href=\"http://www.rackspace.co.uk/sites/default/files/devops-automation-report.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">reading the report</a>! ','Memo to Enterprise IT: DevOps Adoption Is Accelerating ','','publish','closed','closed','','devops-adoption-is-accelerating','','','2014-11-13 13:37:15','2014-11-13 13:37:15','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5143',0,'post','',0),(5154,31,'2014-11-11 11:07:05','2014-11-11 11:07:05','','DevOps Adoption Is Accelerating','','inherit','open','open','','devops-report','','','2014-11-11 11:07:18','2014-11-11 11:07:18','',5143,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/DevOps-Report.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5163,31,'2014-11-11 11:44:22','2014-11-11 11:44:22','DevOps Adoption','DevOps Adoption','','inherit','open','open','','business-team-on-a-professional-training','','','2014-11-11 11:46:18','2014-11-11 11:46:18','',5143,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/DevOps-Blog-Feed.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5172,1,'2014-11-15 21:01:21','2014-11-15 21:01:21','','Cloud management collage AWS map VSPEX','','inherit','open','open','','cloud-management-collage-aws-map-vspex','','','2014-11-15 21:01:21','2014-11-15 21:01:21','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Cloud-management-collage-AWS-map-VSPEX.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5174,1,'2014-11-15 21:35:07','2014-11-15 21:35:07','','ITOP Cloud Resource Screen Shot','','inherit','open','open','','itop-cloud-resource-screen-shot','','','2014-11-15 21:35:36','2014-11-15 21:35:36','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/ITOP-Cloud-Resource-Screen-Shot.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5177,1,'2014-11-15 21:47:12','2014-11-15 21:47:12','','AWS Resources List Video','','inherit','open','open','','aws-resources-list-video','','','2014-11-15 21:47:32','2014-11-15 21:47:32','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/AWS-Resources-List-Video.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5186,31,'2014-11-17 10:45:30','2014-11-17 10:45:30','<section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<h1>User Experience Designer (Enterprise Software, Hyderabad, Telangana)</h1>\r\n<p>Vistara is looking for a user experience designer who will work closely with product management team for understanding features and design highly usable interfaces as per industry trends. The user experience designer will understand the Human-System interactions by creating user personas and scenarios for designing user friendly interfaces. The user experience designer should  be able to measure technical feasibility of the design and translate complex information into easy-to-understand designs and visual elements. This role offers exciting opportunities to conceptualize state of the art features for a leading SaaS solution and be part of a talented team and contribute to a fast growing business.</p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\">Location: </strong></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\">Hyderabad, Telangana</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Reports to:</strong>&nbsp;Senior Director of Product Management</p>\r\n<p>Interested? Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:pm-jobs@vistarait.com\">pm-jobs@vistarait.com</a>.&nbsp;Principals only.<a href=\"mailto:sales@vistarait.com\"><br>\r\n</a></p>\r\n<h2>Desired Experience</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelors or masters in computer science, visual design, or equivalent.</li>\r\n<li>3 or more years of user experience design for web and mobile applications.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding and working knowledge of UI technologies – HTML5, CSS3, JQuery.</li>\r\n<li>Deep working knowledge of design tools like Photoshop, Illustrator, iRise.</li>\r\n<li>Experience with Mac OS and mobile operating systems is an advantage.</li>\r\n<li>Excellent written and oral communication skills.</li>\r\n<li> Strong problem solving skills, time management abilities, and team collaboration aptitude.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b>Who We Are: </b>Vistara provides a comprehensive SaaS solution that delivers IT operations lifecycle management spanning physical, virtual, cloud and application elements. Vistara enables enterprise IT and service providers to see their entire IT infrastructure, control across elements, automate management, and optimize availability, performance and capacity to drive unified IT operations. Headquartered in San Jose, California, Vistara sells directly and through our network of leading distributors and value added resellers. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','User Experience Designer (Enterprise Software, Hyderabad, Telangana)','','publish','open','open','','user-experience-designer-enterprise-software-hyderabad-telangana','','','2014-11-17 10:50:09','2014-11-17 10:50:09','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=5186',0,'page','',0),(5195,31,'2014-11-18 09:28:40','2014-11-18 09:28:40','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div>\r\n</section><section class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"container static-content new-news\" id=\"news-page\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<h1>Press Release</h1>\r\n<div class=\"release-wrap\">\r\n<h2 class=\"name\">Vistara Wins 2014 CRN Tech Innovator Award</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>IT Operations Management Solution Takes Top Honors in the 2014 Managed Services Category; Will Compete for “Editors’ Choice” During the CRN Test Center’s Tech Tank 2014</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><b>San Jose, Calif., Nov 18, 2014</b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\" target=\"_blank\">Vistara</a>, the only SaaS based lifecycle management solution for IT operations, announced today it has been named one of the industry’s leading tech innovators by <a href=\"http://www.crn.com\" target=\"_blank\">CRN</a>. The annual Tech Innovator Awards recognize the companies and products that have used innovation to advance technology, increase productivity, and reduce cost and complexity in ways that provide value to the channel. <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/solutions/managed-service-providers/\" target=\"_blank\">Vistara Lifecycle Management</a> took top honors in the Managed Services category.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Vistara Lifecycle Management enables managed service providers to deliver secure, scalable and compliant IT services to businesses of all sizes. Vistara provides the platform that allows their teams to manage services and assets, automate management, and optimize availability, performance and capacity across customers from a single pane of glass. The multi-tenant SaaS platform offers enterprise-grade security, ease of adoption and maintenance, and massive scalability that allows the providers to focus on their core business - delivering exceptional IT services to their customers.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>“The 2014 Tech Innovator award is testament to Vistara’s proven ability to help managed service providers build profitable lines of business that deliver robust IT services across any IT environment,” says Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer for Vistara. “Our Lifecycle Management solution also empowers managed service providers to manage their clients more effectively and efficiently, while providing them better consistency and insights.”</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.greenpages.com/\" target=\"_blank\">GreenPages-LogicsOne</a>, a leading systems integrator and cloud services company, leverages Vistara Lifecycle Management as part of its Cloud Management as a Service solution. “Vistara enables us to rationalize, consolidate and integrate our customers’ IT operations into a single pane of glass,” says Ron Dupler, CEO of GreenPages-LogicsOne. “That not only allows our customers to be more proactive and responsive to their end users, but also drives efficiency by freeing up their IT staff to focus on more strategic projects and initiatives.”</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>“Solution providers are facing tough challenges as the IT industry continues to evolve at a rapid pace,” said Robert Faletra, CEO of The Channel Company, publisher of CRN.  “Being able to quickly and reliably identify the best new solutions in key technology categories is of great importance to them as they look for innovative ways to earn a competitive advantage. The winners and runners-up in the CRN Tech Innovator Awards represent the best and brightest products and solutions in today’s market, and are some of the most important for solution providers to keep an eye on in the coming year.”</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The annual Tech Innovator Awards are showcased in the December issue of CRN magazine, and the complete list of winners and honorable mentions is online at <a href=\"http://www.crn.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.crn.com</a>. Vistara will also present Vistara Lifecycle Management during the CRN Test Center’s Tech Tank 2014, a “Shark Tank”-style competition where Tech Innovator awardees will compete for “Editors’ Choice” recognition during <a href=\"http://www.nexgencloudcon.com/\" target=\"_blank\">NexGen Cloud Conference & Expo</a>, to be held December 4-5, 2014, in San Diego, Calif. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To learn more about Vistara’s IT platform visit <a title=\"Vistara Home Page\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Follow Vistara at <a title=\"Vistara Blog\" href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/blog/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vistarait.com/blog/</a>; on Twitter at <a title=\"Twitter @VistaraIT\" href=\"https://twitter.com/VistaraIT\" target=\"_blank\">@VistaraIT</a>; and on Facebook at <a title=\"Vistara at Facebook\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VistaraIT\" target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/VistaraIT</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>About Vistara</strong></p>\r\n<p>Headquartered in San Jose, Calif., Vistara provides a comprehensive SaaS solution that enables enterprise IT and service providers to drive unified IT operations management. Vistara manages the end to end IT operations lifecycle for your entire heterogeneous IT environment, and enables IT to provide service centric and business relevant insights. To learn more about Vistara, visit <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com.\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vistarait.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"># # #</p>\r\n<p><strong>About The Channel Company</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Channel Company is the channel community\'s trusted authority for growth and innovation, with established brands including CRN, XChange Events, IPED, and SharedVue. For more than three decades, we have leveraged our proven and leading-edge platforms to deliver prescriptive sales and marketing solutions for the technology channel. The Channel Company provides Communication, Recruitment, Engagement, Enablement, Demand Generation and Intelligence services to drive technology partnerships. Learn more at <a href=\"www.thechannelcompany.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.thechannelcompany.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"># # #</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n<strong>Kevin Wolf</strong>\r\n<p>(650) 327-1641<br>\r\nkevin@tgprllc.com</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Vistara Wins 2014 CRN Tech Innovator Award','','publish','open','open','','vistara-wins-2014-crn-tech-innovator-award','','','2016-09-28 12:39:05','2016-09-28 12:39:05','',1383,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=5195',0,'page','',0),(5201,31,'2014-11-18 10:26:47','2014-11-18 10:26:47','<img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/CRN-Tech-Innovator-Awards-Blog-Post.png\" alt=\"CRN Tech Innovator Awards\" width=\"371\" height=\"224\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-5389\" /></a>We are proud to announce that Vistara has been awarded as <strong>CRN Tech Innovator</strong> in the 2014 Managed Services category. Thank you, CRN!</p> \r\n\r\n<p>The CRN Tech Innovator Award recognizes companies for outstanding innovation in products developed for the enterprise. CRN Test Center editors reviewed hundreds of products across different hardware and software categories to determine the winners.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The award highlights Vistara\'s ability to rationalize, consolidate and integrate IT operations into a single pane of glass. <a href=\"http://www.crn.com/slide-shows/components-peripherals/300074812/the-2014-tech-innovator-awards.htm/pgno/0/33\" target=\"_blank\">As CRN mentioned</a>, Vistara\'s ability to track \"<em>operations from birth to bedtime</em>\" and offer service providers \"<em>a single view of IT operations across on-premise, virtual or cloud systems for multiple clients and locations</em>\" was a key differentiator.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/solutions/managed-service-providers/\" target=\"_blank\">Vistara Lifecycle Management</a> enables solution providers to automate management and optimize availability, performance and capacity across customers. As the only SaaS based lifecycle management solution for IT operations, Vistara unifies IT operations management to help you better deliver exceptional services to customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To learn more about the 2014 CRN Tech Innovator announcement, please read our <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-wins-2014-crn-tech-innovator-award/\" target=\"_blank\">related press release</a></a>.</p>','CRN Names Vistara as Tech Innovator for 2014','','publish','open','open','','crn-names-vistara-tech-innovator','','','2014-12-15 08:47:30','2014-12-15 08:47:30','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5201',0,'post','',0),(5221,31,'2014-11-18 12:17:04','2014-11-18 12:17:04','','CRN Tech Innovator','','inherit','open','open','','crn-tech-innovator-blog-post','','','2014-11-18 12:17:16','2014-11-18 12:17:16','',5201,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/CRN-Tech-Innovator-Blog-Post.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5223,31,'2014-11-18 12:17:35','2014-11-18 12:17:35','','CRN Tech Innovator','','inherit','open','open','','crn-tech-innovator-blog-feed','','','2014-11-18 12:17:44','2014-11-18 12:17:44','',5201,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/CRN-Tech-Innovator-Blog-Feed.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5225,31,'2014-11-18 12:26:11','2014-11-18 12:26:11','','CRN Tech Innovator','','inherit','open','open','','crn-tech-innovator','','','2014-11-18 12:26:20','2014-11-18 12:26:20','',5201,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/CRN-Tech-Innovator.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5228,36,'2014-11-18 12:44:20','2014-11-18 12:44:20','','Slider-9-bg','','inherit','open','open','','slider-9-bg','','','2014-11-18 12:44:20','2014-11-18 12:44:20','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Slider-9-bg.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5229,36,'2014-11-18 12:46:35','2014-11-18 12:46:35','','Learn more button','','inherit','open','open','','learn-more-button','','','2014-11-18 12:46:35','2014-11-18 12:46:35','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Learn-more-button.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5230,36,'2014-11-18 12:48:56','2014-11-18 12:48:56','','CRN-tech-award-2014','','inherit','open','open','','crn-tech-award-2014','','','2014-11-18 12:48:56','2014-11-18 12:48:56','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/CRN-tech-award-2014.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5256,31,'2014-11-20 15:43:11','2014-11-20 15:43:11','<img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/John-Tonthat-Blog-Post.jpg\" alt=\"Cloud Transformation with John Tonthat\" width=\"224\" height=\"336\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-5257\" /> \r\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/jtonthat\" target=\"_blank\">John Tonthat</a> recently joined us as a guest speaker on Vistara\'s <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/resources/latestwebinars/?commid=133615\" target=\"_blank\">Partner Transformation</a> webinar to discuss his perspective on reseller challenges and how they can remain relevant in a cloud services market that\'s expected to reach <strong>$210 billion by 2016</strong>. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>John is Director of Marketing and Business Development at Avnet Technology Solutions where he helps channel partners create cloud solutions to meet their customers\' changing needs. In a freewheeling chat with Vistara\'s marketing director, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/akinaito\" target=\"_blank\">Aki Naito</a>, John told us,</p> \r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>What keeps partners up at night and why,</li>\r\n	<li>How partners should think about extracting value from cloud services,</li>\r\n	<li>The key attributes of channel partners that have successfully made the transition,</li>\r\n        <li>What are the next steps to take <u>today</u></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We\'ll dive into these topics in our next few blogs. In the meantime, watch the <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/resources/latestwebinars/?commid=133615\" target=\"_blank\">fireside chat for John’s practical roadmap</a> on delivering higher-margin cloud solutions to enterprise customers. </p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 1.5em;\">Learn More! </strong></div>\r\nVisit our <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/solutions/managed-service-providers/\" target=\"_blank\">Managed Service Providers</a> page to understand how Vistara can help you increase productivity and deliver robust IT services for your customer base. If you would like to learn more about Vistara, <a href=\"http://info.vistarait.com/vistara-contact-us\">request a live demo</a> today!','Cloud Transformation With John Tonthat','','publish','open','open','','cloud-transformation-with-john-tonthat','','','2014-11-21 04:51:12','2014-11-21 04:51:12','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5256',0,'post','',0),(5257,31,'2014-11-20 15:42:29','2014-11-20 15:42:29','','Cloud Transformation with John Tonthat','','inherit','open','open','','john-tonthat-blog-post','','','2014-11-20 15:42:48','2014-11-20 15:42:48','',5256,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/John-Tonthat-Blog-Post.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5258,31,'2014-11-20 15:42:56','2014-11-20 15:42:56','','Cloud Transformation with John Tonthat','','inherit','open','open','','john-tonthat-blog-feed','','','2014-11-20 15:43:05','2014-11-20 15:43:05','',5256,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/John-Tonthat-Blog-Feed.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5266,31,'2014-11-24 18:33:38','2014-11-24 18:33:38','<p><a href=\"http://www.comptia.org/resources/5th-annual-trends-in-cloud-computing\" target=\"_blank\">CompTIA\'s 5th Annual Trends in Cloud Computing</a> report has an interesting finding about channel partners embracing cloud solutions. Although cloud services are growing more quickly than non-cloud offerings in revenues and profit margins, 59% of solution providers are still struggling to find the right business model for cloud solutions. Channel executives believe coming up with a cloud ready business model is a \"<em>very significant</em>\" challenge ranking it right at the top of their priorities.</p>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/CompTIA-5th-Annual-Study.png\" alt=\"CompTIA 5th Annual Cloud Computing Study\" width=\"478\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignlef size-full wp-image-5269\"/>\r\n\r\n<p>In our recent <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/resources/latestwebinars/?commid=133615\" target=\"_blank\">Partner Transformation</a> webinar, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jtonthat\" target=\"_blank\">John Tonthat</a>, Director of Marketing and Business Development at Avnet Technology Solutions, said that the single biggest issue  partners struggle with is, “How do we survive and expand business operations in the new cloud world?\" John believes that resellers have to build the right set of expertise around hardware, integration, and line-of-business applications to serve customers in a cloud first world.</p> \r\n\r\n<p>Partners should adopt the right methodology that delivers the story, tools, and solutions that are required for cloud transformation projects. Here are John’s takeaways on how solution providers can accelerate success in the cloud:</p> \r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Partners who can leverage the capabilities that virtualization enables and understand the business application stack really well can quickly become trusted advisors.</li>\r\n	<li>Partners need to have a honest conversation by conducting an internal assessment around their capabilities and desire to change before they can begin their cloud transformation journey.</li>\r\n	<li>Analyze the critical role of your distribution partner before joining hands with them. The right solution distributor can not only help you with training and demand generation but also help you close deals.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/resources/latestwebinars/?commid=133615\" target=\"_blank\">Listen to our interactive discussion</a> with John to successfully transition from a commodity infrastructure model to higher margin, value-added cloud solution sales.</p>','How To Survive and Thrive In The Cloud','','publish','open','open','','how-to-survive-and-thrive-in-the-cloud','','','2014-11-25 07:06:36','2014-11-25 07:06:36','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5266',0,'post','',0),(5269,31,'2014-11-24 19:05:05','2014-11-24 19:05:05','','CompTIA 5th Annual Trends in Cloud Computing ','','inherit','open','open','','comptia-5th-annual-study','','','2014-11-24 19:05:46','2014-11-24 19:05:46','',5266,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/CompTIA-5th-Annual-Study.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5279,31,'2014-11-25 07:05:12','2014-11-25 07:05:12','','Partner Transformation','','inherit','open','open','','partner-transformation','','','2014-11-25 07:05:16','2014-11-25 07:05:16','',5266,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Partner-Transformation.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5280,31,'2014-11-25 07:05:29','2014-11-25 07:05:29','','Partner Transformation','','inherit','open','open','','partner-transformation-2','','','2014-11-25 07:05:29','2014-11-25 07:05:29','',5266,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Partner-Transformation1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5287,31,'2014-12-01 12:11:12','2014-12-01 12:11:12','<img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/NexGen-Cloud-Blog-Post.png\" alt=\"NexGen Cloud \" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-5288\" /><p>Join Vistara at <a href=\"http://www.nexgencloudcon.com/\" target=\"_blank\">NexGen Cloud Conference</a> in San Diego this week. CRN has named Vistara as <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/news/vistara-wins-2014-crn-tech-innovator-award/\" target=\"_blank\">2014 IT Innovator for Managed Services</a>. Vistara helps MSPs deliver \"secure, scalable and compliant IT services\" across multiple customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At NexGen Cloud, we will meet with solution providers to discuss how to <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com/company/resources/latestwebinars/?commid=133615\" target=\"_blank\">manage the transformation to a cloud provider</a>. We will also share best practices on how partners can stay competitive in a cloud services market that will hit $210 billion by 2016.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We work with more than hundred partners who use Vistara to deliver exceptional IT services. Meet with us at <strong>Booth #506</strong> to get all the knowledge and advice you need to deliver cloud ready solutions to enterprise customers.</p>  \r\n\r\n<p>We hope to see you there!</p>\r\n\r\n','Join us at NexGen Cloud Conference','','publish','open','open','','join-us-at-nexgen-cloud-conference','','','2014-12-01 12:21:36','2014-12-01 12:21:36','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5287',0,'post','',0),(5288,31,'2014-12-01 12:08:51','2014-12-01 12:08:51','','NexGen Cloud ','','inherit','open','open','','nexgen-cloud-blog-post','','','2014-12-01 12:09:00','2014-12-01 12:09:00','',5287,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/NexGen-Cloud-Blog-Post.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5289,31,'2014-12-01 12:09:13','2014-12-01 12:09:13','','NexGen Cloud ','','inherit','open','open','','nexgen-cloud-blog-feed','','','2014-12-01 12:09:21','2014-12-01 12:09:21','',5287,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/NexGen-Cloud-Blog-Feed.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5297,31,'2014-12-02 09:54:03','2014-12-02 09:54:03','<img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/DevOps-and-Culture-Blog-Post.jpg\" alt=\"DevOps and Culture\" width=\"348\" height=\"230\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-5307\" /><p> Peter Drucker said it best: “Culture eats strategy for breakfast.” Organizational culture matters. Culture is even more critical when enterprises embark on transformational initiatives like DevOps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The <a href=\"http://www.puppetlabs.com/sites/default/files/2014-state-of-devops-report.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">2014 State of DevOps Report</a> found that “organizational culture is one of the strongest predictors of <strong>both IT performance and overall performance</strong> of the organization.” The report found that high-trust organizations encourage better information sharing and smoother collaboration. Culture is the core of DevOps - high-trust firms <strong>deployed 30 times more code</strong> than low performing peers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Saugatuck Technology’s recent publication <a href=\"http://www.saugatucktechnology.com/component/k2/3043-why-devops-matters-practical-insights-on-managing-complex-continuous-change.html\" target=\"_blank\">Why DevOps Matters</a> corroborates this finding. Saugatuck interviewed 300 development and IT operations professionals and managers in the study. Key finding: 71% of respondents only have “pockets of IT automation” with no formal DevOps strategy in place. The biggest factor holding back DevOps adoption is \"established cultural habits.\"</p>     \r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Challenges-in-Implementing-DevOps.png\" alt=\"Challenges in Implementing DevOps\" width=\"971\" height=\"554\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-5304\" />\r\n \r\n<p>The report asks IT leaders to break down organizational silos when building a DevOps culture. Here are five best practices from the survey:</p>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n       <li><strong>Start small</strong>. Embrace DevOps with a small engagement. Create a virtual Center of Excellence that will create consistent practices across different initiatives.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Training</strong>. Bring in a mix of internal and external trainers to create a shared organizational culture. Training sessions enhance collaboration and trust among IT leadership, Ops, and Dev teams.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Automation</strong>. Automation through a DevOps toolset will increase release velocity and enhance organizational maturity.</li>\r\n         <li><strong>Measure business results</strong>. DevOps teams are most successful when they tie outcomes to broader organizational performance. Take the help of business stakeholders to define success metrics for every project.</li>\r\n         <li><strong>Continuous improvement</strong>. Culture is never at rest. Constantly check and improve execution at all levels.</li>    \r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://saugatucktechnology.com/images/Thought%20Leadership/Saugatuck_Paper-DevOps-06Oct2014.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Read the report</a> to understand why you need to engineer the right culture before starting your DevOps journey.</p>','DevOps Is All About Changing Organizational Culture ','','publish','open','open','','devops-is-all-about-organizational-culture','','','2014-12-02 10:11:51','2014-12-02 10:11:51','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5297',0,'post','',0),(5304,31,'2014-12-02 10:04:35','2014-12-02 10:04:35','','Challenges in Implementing DevOps','','inherit','open','open','','challenges-in-implementing-devops','','','2014-12-02 10:04:44','2014-12-02 10:04:44','',5297,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/Challenges-in-Implementing-DevOps.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5307,31,'2014-12-02 10:09:46','2014-12-02 10:09:46','','DevOps and Culture','','inherit','open','open','','business-handshake','','','2014-12-02 10:10:01','2014-12-02 10:10:01','',5297,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/DevOps-and-Culture-Blog-Post.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5308,31,'2014-12-02 10:10:12','2014-12-02 10:10:12','','DevOps and Culture','','inherit','open','open','','business-handshake-2','','','2014-12-02 10:10:23','2014-12-02 10:10:23','',5297,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/DevOps-and-Culture-Blog-Feed.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(5313,31,'2014-12-04 10:02:11','2014-12-04 10:02:11','<img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/IT-Operations-Predictions-Blog-Post.png\" alt=\"IT Operations Predictions\" width=\"393\" height=\"224\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-5320\" /><p>It’s that time of the year again when analyst firms release their end-of-year predictions. We’ll be reading and dissecting what these predictions mean for IT leaders in the coming year.</p> \r\n\r\n<p>Gartner’s <a href=\"https://www.gartner.com/doc/2927417\" target=\"_blank\">Predicts 2015: IT Operations Management</a> highlights the growing importance of <a href=\"http://www.gartner.com/technology/research/digital-business/\" target=\"_blank\">digital business</a> transformation. Here are three great takeaways from the report:</p>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n         <li><strong>Stop fighting Shadow IT</strong>. Gartner analyst <a href=\"http://www.gartner.com/analyst/38357/BiswajeetMahapatra\" target=\"_blank\">Biswajeet Mahapatra</a> has wise advice for IT execs. IT leaders need to embrace shadow IT and integrate it into their organizational processes. Absorbing shadow IT will help enterprises “<strong>reduce costs and control service quality.</strong>” IT will embrace the role of <em>brokers</em> for driving the consumption of enterprise services.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Demonstrate business relevance</strong>. IT Ops has long failed to establish their contribution to business outcomes. Researcher <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jeffinthefm\" target=\"_blank\">Jeff Brooks</a> writes that IT leaders “struggle to know <strong>what the business uses to measure success</strong>.” IT chiefs will increasingly use business value dashboards for communicating their performance. Business value dashboards enable IT to “identify what activities and services can have the most impact on what the business cares about.”</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Focus on application monitoring</strong>. Legacy monitoring technologies are unable to manage today\'s application footprint. Enterprises are building applications with technologies like PHP, Scala and Ruby using agile methodologies. IT teams need to adopt new monitoring architectures that are “inherently tied to the business.” Application monitoring tools offer enterprises the \"<strong>ability to measure and understand key business transactions and user experience</strong>\" which is critical to differentiation.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Gartner’s <a href=\"https://www.gartner.com/doc/2927417\" target=\"_blank\">complete research report</a> is available for purchase on their site.</p>\r\n','Gartner’s Crystal Ball for IT Operations in 2015 and Beyond','','publish','open','open','','gartners-crystal-ball-for-it-operations','','','2014-12-08 18:16:38','2014-12-08 18:16:38','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?p=5313',0,'po