n writing exercise</strong> to demonstrate their writing ability.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong skills in using Microsoft Office suite and online collaboration solutions such as Google Docs.</li>\r\n	<li>Work from <strong>5.30 PM to 2.30 AM</strong> India time to align with sales and marketing teams in US time zones.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b>Who We Are: </b>Vistara provides a comprehensive SaaS solution that delivers IT operations lifecycle management spanning physical, virtual, cloud and application elements. Vistara enables enterprise IT and service providers to see their entire IT infrastructure, control across elements, automate management, and optimize availability, performance and capacity to drive unified IT operations. Headquartered in San Jose, California, Vistara sells directly and through our network of leading distributors and value added resellers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Sales Development Representative (Enterprise Software, Hyderabad, Telangana)','','publish','open','open','','sales-development-representative-enterprise-software-hyderabad-telangana','','','2015-01-21 07:15:03','2015-01-21 07:15:03','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=5476',0,'page','',0),(5526,36,'2015-02-16 13:08:56','2015-02-16 13:08:56','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\" class=\"leafnode-nav\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div>\r\n</section><section id=\"infographic-banner-plain\">\r\n<div class=\"page-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h1>Infographic – 15 DevOps Influencers</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<div id=\"unified-operations\">\r\n<section id=\"casestudy-page\" class=\"section-white\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/DevOps-Influencers-Infographic-600x.jpg\"/><br><hr>\r\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/share\" class=\"twitter-share-button alignright\" data-url=\"http://hubs.ly/y0x6J70\" data-text=