>\r\n<li>The Sales Engineer (SE) provides pre-sales technical support to Vistara Sales Reps (SR) and customers covering all of the company’s family of products.</li>\r\n<li>The SE and SR work in tandem to formulate account strategies.</li>\r\n<li>The SE makes pre-sales calls on prospective clients, participates in local and regional seminars, and acts as the technical account manager for existing customers.</li>\r\n<li>The SE is the focal point for customer evaluations, proof of concepts, and demos.</li>\r\n<li>The SE is expected to stay abreast of current industry technology, trends, and competition.</li>\r\n<li>The SE will spend a considerable amount of time talking in front of customers in small (round table) discussions as well as large (seminar) audiences.</li>\r\n<li>The SE will work in tandem with the SR(s) in fulfilling sales goals and responding to RFI/RFPs.</li>\r\n<li>The SE may act as a focal point in case of a technical post-sales escalation for current customers. Some travel will be required.</li>\r\n<li>The SE will perform system deployment, installation, and integration of Vistara solutions in customer environments.</li>\r\n<li>SE’S should be self-motivated, able to work well with multiple sales reps, and be creative in obtaining information and solving problems.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br>\r\n<h3>Required Experience</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>5 years plus of experience supporting IT solutions into Mid-market, large enterprise accounts and complex organizations using consultative sales techniques.</li>\r\n<li>5 years plus of infrastructure experience</li>\r\n<li>BS/BA in CS/EE a plus</li>\r\n<li>Strong Windows & VMWare skills</li>\r\n<li>Familiarity with infrastructure related solutions from other competitors</li>\r\n<li>The SE must have excellent written and verbal communications skills</li>\r\n<li>The SE must be able to talk about technical subjects and deliver technical presentation to a wide array of audiences with both technical and non-technical backgrounds</li>\r\n<li>The SE must be able to transfer knowledge to inexperienced customers and VAR’s</li>\r\n<li>The SE must have a desire to learn new technologies and enjoy doing “hands-on” work with Vistara technology and other relevant technologies</li>\r\n<li>The SE must possess various personal traits like excellent inter-personal skills, high energy, flexible, self- motivated, trustworthy, team player and dependable</li>\r\n<li>Has excellent follow through skills</li>\r\n<li>Must have experience with various operating systems including LINUX and Windows from a Systems Administrator perspective</li>\r\n<li>Understanding of infrastructure monitoring and management</li>\r\n<li>Travel 25-75%</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\"><div class=\"widget-wrap\"><h3>Share this job</h3><div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div></div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Sales Engineer','','publish','closed','closed','','salesengineer','','','2016-08-19 10:58:58','2016-08-19 10:58:58','',6469,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=6485',0,'page','',0),(6491,36,'2016-07-18 14:25:43','2016-07-18 14:25:43','<section id=\"inner-spotlight-new\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">[shortmenu menu=\"who-we-are\" enhance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div>\r\n</section><section id=\"careers-page-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"page-banner\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h1>Senior JavaScript Engineer</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class=\"section-white\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n\r\n<p>We are looking for an experienced JavaScript engineer who will be responsible for building our next-generation hybrid cloud management platform.</p>\r\n<dl id=\"careerspage\">\r\n 	<dt><strong>Location</strong>: Hyderabad, TS</dt>\r\n 	<dt><strong>Interested?</strong> Email a resume in reverse chronological format to <a href=\"mailto:careers@vistarait.com\">careers@vistarait.com</a>. Principals only.</dt