hance=\"true\" arrow=\"false\"]</div>\r\n</section><section class=\"section\">\r\n<div id=\"news-page\" class=\"container static-content new-news\">\r\n<div class=\"press-left\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<h1>Press Release</h1>\r\n<div class=\"release-wrap\">\r\n<h2 class=\"name\">Vistara to Demonstrate Modern IT Operations Management Platform at AWS re:Invent 2016</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><strong>The SaaS-based system allows enterprises and service providers to embrace the cloud with confidence</strong></p><br/>\r\n<p><b>SAN JOSE, CA--(Marketwired - Nov 22, 2016)</b> - <a href=\"http://www.vistarait.com\" target=\"_blank\">Vistara</a> will showcase its IT operations management platform at AWS re:Invent 2016. The SaaS-based system enables enterprise IT operations teams to scale, optimize and take full advantage of modern cloud services. Thousands of customers with hybrid cloud infrastructures already use Vistara to obtain the flexibility of public clouds, without sacrificing operational integrity. Vistara will be in booth #112.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p>\"Enterprises are increasingly leveraging cloud platforms like AWS for greater elasticity and scalability,\" says Varma Kunaparaju, Chief Technology Officer at Vistara. \"IT teams want contextual visibility, policy-driven automation and dynamic service management across on-premises, private and public cloud environments. Vistara has been specifically designed to meet this operational and business need. As a leading IT operations management platform, it\'s our mission to rapidly support critical AWS services.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p>\"IT operations teams are always optimizing the performance of mission-critical applications across hybrid clouds,\" continues Kunaparaju. \"At re:Invent, we will demonstrate how Vistara\'s policy-driven framework can provide true business value. It enables enterprises and managed service providers to proactively manage hybrid environments and automate routine operational tasks at web-scale. With Vistara, IT operations teams can drive innovation, productivity and insights across the enterprise.\"</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p>To schedule an appointment with a Vistara cloud expert, email <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:events@vistarait.com\">events@vistarait.com</a> or visit <a href=\"https://www.vistarait.com/aws-reinvent/\">www.vistarait.com/aws-reinvent</a>.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p><strong>About Vistara</strong></p>\r\n<p>Vistara\'s IT operations management platform changes enterprise IT operations from a cost center to a value-creation engine. By providing a contextual view of any IT environment, policy-based automation and dynamic management, and a shared services approach across business units, Vistara is the leading choice for modern IT operations management. To learn more, visit <a href=\"https://www.vistarait.com\">www.vistarait.com</a>. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"press-right\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Share this page</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner social-inner\">[ssba]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"widget-wrap\">\r\n<h3>Media Contact</h3>\r\n<div class=\"widget-inner\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Kevin Wolf</strong>\r\n<p>(650) 327-1641<br>\r\nkevin@tgprllc.com</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>','Vistara to Demonstrate Modern IT Operations Management Platform at AWS re:Invent 2016','','publish','closed','closed','','vistara-awsreinvent','','','2016-11-23 04:48:00','2016-11-23 04:48:00','',1383,'http://www.vistarait.com/?page_id=6689',0,'page','',0),(6699,36,'2017-01-18 05:46:59','2017-01-18 05:46:59','','15-stats-for-IT-Operations-Professional-800x','','inherit','open','closed','','15-stats-for-it-operations-professional-800x','','','2017-01-18 05:46:59','2017-01-18 05:46:59','',0,'http://www.vistarait.com/wp-content/uploads/15-stats-for-IT-Operations-Professional-800x.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(6700,36,'2017-01-20 09:17:45','2017-01-20 09:17:45','','VIstara For Retail',